1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:38,170
百萬  美元  寶貝

2
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:47,360
加油
Do it!

3
00:00:50,680 --> 00:00:51,870
你能打敗他！你能打敗他！
You got him! You got him!

4
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:09,290
我只遇見過一個我不想和他爭斗的人
I only ever met one man I wouldn't wanna fight.

5
00:01:09,470 --> 00:01:11,060
我止不了血
I can't stop that.

6
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,030
滾開吧，你個沒有的東西
Get out of here, you useless tit.

7
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:16,170
我遇見他的時候 他已經是拳擊界最好的傷口護理師
When I met him, he was already the best cut man in the business.

8
00:01:16,340 --> 00:01:17,570
你能止住嗎？
Can you stop it?

9
00:01:17,740 --> 00:01:21,070
從60年代起就開始做訓練師和經理人 一直保持著高昂的熱情
Started training and managing in the '60s, but he never lost his gift.

10
00:01:21,310 --> 00:01:22,830
不行
No.

11
00:01:30,490 --> 00:01:32,280
我來看看他
Let me have a look at him.

12
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:34,110
他沒事，他沒事
He's fine. He's fine.

13
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,580
如果你止不了血的話就不是沒事
He ain't if you don't stop this bleeding.

14
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:38,360
我再給你一個回合
I'll give you one more round.

15
00:01:40,130 --> 00:01:43,430
- 時間到了，來吧    - 我們怎么辦？告訴我怎么辦
- Seconds out. Let's go.    - What do we do? Tell me what to do.

16
00:01:44,370 --> 00:01:45,630
你讓他打你
You let him hit you.

17
00:01:49,270 --> 00:01:51,870
有時你就是無能為力
Sometimes there's just nothing you can do.

18
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:55,200
傷口太深, 離骨頭太近
Cut's too wide, too close to the bone.

19
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:57,970
也許是斷了一條血管...
Maybe you got a severed vein...

20
00:01:58,180 --> 00:02:00,880
...或者你就是無法讓止血藥深入里面
...or you just can't get the coagulant deep enough.

21
00:02:02,020 --> 00:02:03,490
- 加油！    - 分開，分開
- Come on!    - Break. Break.

22
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:06,320
在肌肉的不同層次
There are all kinds of combinations you come up against...

23
00:02:06,490 --> 00:02:08,720
你會遇到各種不同的問題組合
...down in the different layers of meat...

24
00:02:08,890 --> 00:02:10,790
而弗蘭基全都知道如何解決
...and Frankie knew how to work every one.

25
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:22,600
- 對！加油！    - 你在做什么？
- That's it! Come on!    - What are you doing?

26
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:29,000
打倒他，威利！
Knock him out, Willie!

27
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,450
人們熱愛暴力
People love violence.

28
00:02:40,390 --> 00:02:43,020
他們會在車禍現場 減慢車速查看死尸
They'll slow down at a car wreck to check for bodies.

29
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:45,460
就是這些人宣稱他們熱愛拳擊
Same people claim to love boxing.

30
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,960
他們根本不了解拳擊是什么
They got no idea what it is.

31
00:02:48,530 --> 00:02:50,620
拳擊是有關尊嚴
Boxing is about respect.

32
00:02:51,170 --> 00:02:52,630
贏得你自己的...
Getting it for yourself...

33
00:02:53,300 --> 00:02:56,140
...同時剝奪對手的
...and taking it away from the other guy.

34
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:01,510
我先去發動車
I'll warm up the car.

35
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,110
鄧先生？
Mr.Dunn?

36
00:03:03,980 --> 00:03:05,280
我欠你錢？
I owe you money?

37
00:03:05,450 --> 00:03:06,710
沒有，先生
No, sir.

38
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,370
我認識你媽媽？
I know your mama?

39
00:03:08,620 --> 00:03:10,680
這個我確實不知道，先生
Don't rightly know, sir.

40
00:03:10,850 --> 00:03:13,320
- 那你想干什么？    - 我參加了墊場賽
- Then what is it you want?    - I was on the undercard.

41
00:03:13,490 --> 00:03:16,080
而且我也贏了 我是麥琪 菲斯杰拉德
I won my fight too. Maggie Fitzgerald.

42
00:03:16,260 --> 00:03:18,820
那么，麥琪 菲斯杰拉德，有什么事嗎？
Well, Maggie Fitzgerald, what's up?

43
00:03:19,330 --> 00:03:21,350
- 你有沒有正好看了我的比賽？    - 沒有
- Did you happen to see it?    - Nope.

44
00:03:21,530 --> 00:03:22,960
我干的不錯
I did pretty good.

45
00:03:23,130 --> 00:03:25,620
我想你也許有興趣訓練我
Thought you might be interested in training me.

46
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,530
我不訓練女孩子
I don't train girls.

47
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:31,160
也許你應該試試 看我打過的人都說我很兇狠
Maybe you should. People see me fight say I'm pretty tough.

48
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:35,210
小姐, 光是兇狠并不夠
Girlie, tough ain't enough.

49
00:03:48,260 --> 00:03:50,230
這是個錯誤
It's a mistake.

50
00:03:55,730 --> 00:03:57,560
車應該能向后退的，弗蘭基
Car should be able to back up, Frankie.

51
00:03:58,170 --> 00:04:00,230
幫我推一下，行不？
Just push, will you?

52
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:04,030
- 霍根有什么事？    - 邀請我們參加頭銜戰
- What did Hogan want?    - Offered us a title shot.

53
00:04:04,740 --> 00:04:06,070
是時候了
About time.

54
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,210
我直接把他拒絕了
I turned him down flat.

55
00:04:08,410 --> 00:04:11,810
再多打兩三場比賽 你就準備充分了
Two or three more fights, you'll be ready.

56
00:04:15,790 --> 00:04:19,280
好久以前就說是兩三場比賽了，弗蘭基
Been two or three more fights for a long time now, Frankie.

57
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:21,850
聽著，威利 你只有一次機會贏得冠軍
Look, Willie, you get one shot at the title.

58
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:24,020
輸掉的話 可能就再沒有機會了
You lose it, it may not come around again.

59
00:04:24,690 --> 00:04:28,030
再多打兩三場比賽 我們就準備充分了
Now, two or three more fights and we'll be ready.

60
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,860
都聽你的，弗蘭基
Whatever you say, Frankie.

61
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:35,860
弗蘭基總喜歡說 拳擊是一種不自然的運動
Frankie liked to say that boxing is an unnatural act...

62
00:04:36,210 --> 00:04:39,140
因為拳擊中的每樣東西都是逆向的
...that everything in boxing is backwards.

63
00:04:40,810 --> 00:04:42,370
有時...
Sometimes...

64
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:46,280
...打出一記重拳 的最好方法是退后一步
...best way to deliver a punch is step back.

65
00:04:55,020 --> 00:04:57,720
我的主啊，請盡力...
Well, do your best, Lord...

66
00:04:58,260 --> 00:05:00,090
...保護凱蒂
...protect Katy.

67
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:02,760
還有安妮
Annie too.

68
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:05,220
至于其他的...
Other than that...

69
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:09,370
...你知道我想要什么 所以我再重復也沒有什么用
...you know what I want, there's no use me repeating myself.

70
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:14,400
但是退后太多 你就已經退出比賽了
But step back too far, you ain't fighting at all.

71
00:05:24,510 --> 00:05:26,260
（圣馬可教堂）

72
00:05:30,530 --> 00:05:32,990
- 再見    - 再見
- Bye.    - Bye.

73
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:36,790
神父，布道很精彩，讓我流淚
Father, that was a great sermon. Made me weep.

74
00:05:36,970 --> 00:05:38,430
你這周又有什么疑惑？
What's confusing you this week?

75
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:41,070
噢，就是那個老掉牙的三位一體的問題
Oh, it's the same old one-God-three-God thing.

76
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:44,470
弗蘭基, 大多數人幼兒園的時候 就知道一切都是信心的問題
Frankie, most people figure out by kindergarten it's about faith.

77
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:49,130
是不是有點象三種不一樣的薩其馬 都裝在一個大盒子里？
Is it sort of like Snap, Crackle and Pop all rolled up in one big box?

78
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:53,510
你站在我的教堂外面 把上帝比做點心？
You're standing outside my church comparing God to Rice Krispies?

79
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:56,450
你來做彌撒的唯一原因 就是要騷擾我
The only reason you come to Mass is to wind me up.

80
00:05:56,620 --> 00:05:58,680
- 不過今天不會了    - 我有點迷惑
- It won't happen this morning.    - I'm confused.

81
00:05:58,850 --> 00:06:00,150
- 不，你沒有    - 不，我有
- No, you aren't.    - Yes, I am.

82
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:03,520
那好，我給你的答案是： 只有一位上帝
Then here's your answer: There's one God.

83
00:06:03,690 --> 00:06:05,160
還有事嗎？我很忙
Anything else? Because I'm busy.

84
00:06:05,330 --> 00:06:08,160
- 那么圣靈呢？    - 他是上帝的愛的一種表現形式
- What about the Holy Ghost?    - He's an expression of God's love.

85
00:06:08,330 --> 00:06:10,920
- 耶穌呢？    - 上帝之子，別在這兒裝傻了
- And Jesus?    - Son of God. Don't play stupid.

86
00:06:11,130 --> 00:06:13,470
那么他是什么呢？ 上帝的兒子意味著半神半人？
What is he then? Does that make him a demigod?

87
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:16,000
沒有半神半人 操他媽的異教徒！
There are no demigods, you fucking pagan!

88
00:06:22,380 --> 00:06:24,350
- 給你女兒寫信了么？    - 當然
- Did you write your daughter?    - Absolutely.

89
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:26,070
你這是對一個神父撒謊
Now you're lying to a priest.

90
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:29,810
跟你說吧，休息一天 明天別來了
You know what? Take a day off, don't come to Mass tomorrow.

91
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,480
（斗場拳擊館）

92
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:44,360
有些人會說對于一個拳手來說 最重要的莫過于熱情
Some people would say the most important thing a fighter can have is heart.

93
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:48,370
弗蘭基則會說 “給我一個只有熱情的拳手...
Frankie would say, "Show me a fighter who's nothing but heart...

94
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:51,700
...我會告訴他什么叫鼻青臉腫”
...and I'll show you a man waiting for a beating."

95
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:03,480
我想我只見過一個全心投入的拳手
Think I only ever met one fighter who was all heart.

96
00:07:04,850 --> 00:07:08,350
我的名號是“戰斗小子” 丹吉爾 迪拉德 巴奇...
My name's Dangerous Dillard Fighting Flippo Bam-Bam Barch...

97
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,390
...來自德克薩斯布勞德縣！
...out of Broward County, T exas!

98
00:07:12,860 --> 00:07:15,960
丹吉爾是幾年前來的
Danger showed up a couple of years back.

99
00:07:17,330 --> 00:07:21,830
他和他媽媽的新男友艾瑞威爾 一起到洛杉磯來
He'd come visiting L.A. With Ervel, his mama's new boyfriend.

100
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:27,270
似乎艾瑞威爾迷了路 自己回去了德克薩斯
Apparently Ervel got lost and ended up back in Texas.

101
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:32,040
在來這里以前 丹吉爾找了他大概一個星期
Danger looked for him for about a week before he introduced himself.

102
00:07:34,250 --> 00:07:38,950
嘿，你知道么 我對黑鬼從來沒有任何偏見
Hey, you know, I gots nothing against niggers.

103
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:42,390
呃，真高興聽你這么說
Well, that's nice to hear.

104
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:46,810
嗯，我的家鄉很多人確實是那樣...
Yeah, lots of people where I comes from does...

105
00:07:46,810 --> 00:07:50,570
...但是我媽媽告訴我 不要傷害任何人...
...but my mama taught me not to cause hurt to no man...

106
00:07:50,570 --> 00:07:52,470
...不管是不是黑鬼
...niggers or not.

107
00:07:52,470 --> 00:07:55,230
你媽媽還真是個好人 我可以幫你點什么嘛？
You got a nice mama. Anything else I can do for you?

108
00:07:55,230 --> 00:07:57,660
你也許只是隨便問個問題  ...
Just one of those questions you ask...

109
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:59,990
...但是丹吉爾總想給你最好的答案
...but Danger wanted to give it his best answer.

110
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:04,570
我想成為次中量級世界冠軍
Well, sir, I'd likes to become the welterweight champion of the world.

111
00:08:06,010 --> 00:08:09,340
我要挑戰“城市機動眼鏡蛇”...
And I challenge the Motor City Cobra...

112
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:11,200
...還有“刺客”湯馬斯 赫爾斯...
...Thomas "Hit Man" Hearns...

113
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:15,460
...爭奪次中量級世界冠軍！
...to fight me for the welterweight championship of the whole world!

114
00:08:15,460 --> 00:08:18,690
冒失鬼，閉嘴 你連排名都沒有
Yo, Flip, shut up, man! You ain't even ranked.

115
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:21,240
你最少要打一場比賽才能有排名
You gotta have at least one fight to be ranked.

116
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:24,010
嘿，我可以和任何人打，隨時！
Hey, I'll fight any man, anytime!

117
00:08:24,010 --> 00:08:25,840
嘿，你是個壞蛋，是嗎？
Hey, you a bad man, huh?

118
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:28,460
進繩圈里來，我陪你玩一回合
Get in the ring. Go a round with me.

119
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:31,370
- 謝瑞爾    - 沒問題
- Shawrelle.    - I will.

120
00:08:31,370 --> 00:08:33,910
別理他
Leave him alone.

121
00:08:34,220 --> 00:08:37,370
丹吉爾, 你繼續訓練
Danger, you go on back to training.

122
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:40,240
我會的，斯科雷普先生
Will do, Mr.Scrap.

123
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:45,820
你的緊身褲不錯
Them's some nice tights, Danger.

124
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:48,600
我以后再揍你的屁股 小妞
I'll give you that ass-whupping later, Olive Oyl.

125
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:51,000
你的褲子還真不賴，丹吉爾
Hey, bro, those pants look real pretty on you.

126
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,830
把他媽媽的緊身衣還給她吧
Give his mama back her tights.

127
00:08:52,830 --> 00:08:57,020
謝瑞爾 貝里的左鉤拳 可以打飛一輛坦克 ...
Shawrelle Berry had a left hook that would move a tank...

128
00:08:57,020 --> 00:09:00,250
...但是他的心胸卻象豆子一樣小
...but he had a heart the size of a split pea.

129
00:09:00,250 --> 00:09:04,380
弗蘭基17年前從巴比 馬龍 手里買下了斗場拳擊館
Frankie bought the Hit Pit from Bobby Malone 17 years ago.

130
00:09:04,380 --> 00:09:08,170
巴比想搬到佛羅里達去 而弗蘭基想要生活有點保障
Bobby wanted to move to Florida, and Frankie wanted some security.

131
00:09:08,170 --> 00:09:11,130
巴比在他收拾行李的時候死掉了
Bobby died while he was packing.

132
00:09:11,130 --> 00:09:15,160
弗蘭基那時候才發現 大多數拳擊館都虧錢
And Frankie found out most gyms lose money.

133
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:18,380
我想我已經告訴過你 別讓丹吉爾繼續訓練下去了
I thought I told you I didn't want Danger working out here anymore.

134
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:20,610
他又不會傷害到別人，弗蘭基
He ain't hurting nothing, Frankie.

135
00:09:20,610 --> 00:09:22,170
他傷害到我了
Well, he's hurting me.

136
00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:27,060
我看著心疼 看他朝著空氣揮拳，好象空氣會反擊一樣
Breaking my heart, watching him punch the air like he thinks it's gonna punch back.

137
00:09:27,060 --> 00:09:30,160
還有我告訴你多少次了 漂白液就是漂白液
And how many times have I gotta tell you that bleach is bleach?

138
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:33,920
你就不能買便宜點的么？ 不用買貴的那種
Why can't you buy the cheap stuff? You don't have to buy the expensive stuff.

139
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:36,120
這種更好聞一些，弗蘭基
It smells better, Frankie.

140
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:39,270
漂白液聞起來還是漂白液
Bleach smells like bleach.

141
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:51,490
- 嘿，斯科雷普    - 嘿，威利先生
- Hey, Scrap.    - Hey, Mr.Willie.

142
00:09:52,890 --> 00:09:55,780
嘿，昨晚打得不錯
Hey, nice fight last night.

143
00:09:59,610 --> 00:10:01,900
打得不錯
Nice fight.

144
00:10:04,370 --> 00:10:06,890
- 大個子威利    - 嘿，賽利
- Big Willie.    - Hey, Sally.

145
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,930
- 打得不錯    - 謝了，兄弟
- Nice fight.    - Thanks, man.

146
00:10:10,930 --> 00:10:13,500
有人在談話
People are talking.

147
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:31,770
這他媽的是什么語言？
What the hell kind of language is that?

148
00:10:31,770 --> 00:10:33,640
你想干嗎？
What do you want?

149
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:36,810
我想你可能想知道 你有一個拳手...
I thought you might like to know you got a fighter out there...

150
00:10:36,810 --> 00:10:39,460
...不跟別的經理人說話
...not talking to another manager.

151
00:10:40,190 --> 00:10:42,270
不跟別的經理人說話？
Not talking to another manager?

152
00:10:42,270 --> 00:10:44,830
不是隨便什么經理人
And not just any manager.

153
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:47,600
米奇 麥克
Mickey Mack.

154
