307
00:22:41,850 --> 00:22:44,150
不，拿著吧
No, take the bag.

308
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:47,150
反正我都二十年沒見過它了
I haven't seen it in 20 years anyway.

309
00:22:47,150 --> 00:22:51,720
我還有三個 好好享受它，好嗎？
I've had three since then. Just enjoy it, will you?

310
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:54,860
- 我只是在自己買之前暫時借用一下    - 嗯
- I'll just borrow it till I buy my own.    - Yeah.

311
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:57,470
別丟了就行
Just don't lose it.

312
00:23:05,580 --> 00:23:07,280
對，我知道，霍根...
Yeah, I know, Hogan...

313
00:23:07,280 --> 00:23:10,250
...你的拳手是冠軍 所以我們不能對半分...
...your guy's the champ, so we don't split 50s...

314
00:23:10,250 --> 00:23:13,410
...但是如果我連四成--
...but if I don't see 40 percent...

315
00:23:13,790 --> 00:23:18,160
聽著，你同意六四開的時候再給我電話 要不然就別打來了
Look, you call me back when it's 60-40 or don't call me back at all.

316
00:23:27,340 --> 00:23:29,640
- 嘿，威利    - 嘿，弗蘭基
- Hey, Willie.    - Hey, Frankie.

317
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,410
出什么事情了么？
Something wrong?

318
00:23:31,410 --> 00:23:35,770
對不起我就這么來找您 我知道你不喜歡別人來串門
I'm sorry to come by your house like this. I know you don't like people dropping in.

319
00:23:35,940 --> 00:23:39,310
噢，你可不是外人，威利 什么時候來我都歡迎，進來吧
Oh, you're not people, Willie. You're welcome anytime. Come on in.

320
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:42,020
我是來謝謝您幫格蕾斯把車拿回來
I wanted to thank you for getting Gracie's car back.

321
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:44,020
哦，你不用謝我
Oh, well, you don't have to thank me.

322
00:23:44,020 --> 00:23:48,720
為自己的車多花1000美元 也不算幫什么忙
Paying an extra thousand dollars for your own car ain't exactly a favor.

323
00:23:48,890 --> 00:23:50,460
格蕾斯看見那輛車的時候都哭了
Gracie cried when she saw it.

324
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:52,590
真的？
Really?

325
00:23:53,530 --> 00:23:55,690
我還想跟您談談業務上的事情
I also needed to talk with you about business.

326
00:23:55,860 --> 00:23:59,890
噢，對了，我剛和霍根通了電話 九月份的冠軍賽都談好了
Oh, yeah, well, I just got off the phone with Hogan. We're all set for September.

327
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:01,900
除了分成的問題
Everything but the split.

328
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:03,930
我得離開你了，弗蘭基
I gotta leave you, Frankie.

329
00:24:06,210 --> 00:24:07,440
什么？
What?

330
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:14,140
威利，再打兩場就到冠軍賽了
Willie, the title's just two fights away.

331
00:24:14,320 --> 00:24:18,550
不是這個問題，是-- 就好象你說的, 我只有一次機會
It ain't that, it's... It's like you said, I got one shot.

332
00:24:19,150 --> 00:24:21,640
如果我贏了，我就可以在我還能掙 的時候掙盡可能多的錢
If I win, I gotta make as much as I can while I can.

333
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:25,590
我需要有人能幫我實現
I need somebody in the action who can make things happen.

334
00:24:26,560 --> 00:24:29,390
而且我得在比賽前換經理人
And I gotta make the change before the fight.

335
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:32,970
他說必須讓他帶我去打冠軍賽 他才會簽下我
Only way this guy say he'd take me is if he took me to the title.

336
00:24:33,570 --> 00:24:37,030
所以我給你安排冠軍賽 然后他帶你去參加
So I get you the title fight, and this guy takes you there?

337
00:24:37,210 --> 00:24:38,430
他說必須這樣
Only way he'd do it.

338
00:24:39,370 --> 00:24:43,140
很抱歉，弗蘭基 我知道你等冠軍很久了
I'm sorry, Frankie. I know how long you waiting on a title.

339
00:24:43,340 --> 00:24:44,830
我也希望能和你一起
I wish it could've been with me.

340
00:24:46,650 --> 00:24:50,640
米奇 麥克是個生意人 他什么也教不了你
Mickey Mack's a businessman. He can't teach you nothing.

341
00:24:51,420 --> 00:24:53,650
你已經教會了一切我需要知道的
You already taught me everything I need to know.

342
00:25:02,260 --> 00:25:05,200
有些話人們永遠都不愿意聽
There's some things people just don 't want to hear.

343
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:20,810
我要挑戰“城市機動眼鏡蛇” 還有“刺客”湯馬斯 赫爾斯...
And I challenge the Motor City Cobra, Thomas "Hit Man" Hearns...

344
00:25:20,980 --> 00:25:25,280
......爭奪次中量級世界冠軍！
...to fight me for the welterweight championship of the whole world.

345
00:25:25,450 --> 00:25:28,150
丹吉爾，我這個拳套不是白戴的
Danger, I'm wearing these mitts for a reason.

346
00:25:29,460 --> 00:25:32,320
只是練習一下我的步伐 斯科雷普先生
Just working on my footwork, Mr.Scrap.

347
00:25:33,090 --> 00:25:37,030
丹吉爾，你打一拳 要不然就滾出去
Danger, you throw a punch or get the hell out of this gym.

348
00:25:41,440 --> 00:25:44,870
丹吉爾，好好想想那一拳 我馬上就回來
Danger, while you thinking about that punch, I'll be right back.

349
00:25:46,240 --> 00:25:50,300
我想我會狠狠打那一拳，斯科雷普先生
I'm thinking how I'm gonna hit it hard for you, Mr.Scrap.

350
00:25:55,320 --> 00:26:01,550
沒人忍心告訴丹吉爾 赫爾斯好多年前就已經退休了
No one had the heart to tell Danger that Hearns retired years ago.

351
00:26:08,830 --> 00:26:10,890
威利的事情我聽說了
I heard about Willie.

352
00:26:11,330 --> 00:26:14,230
非常無情，太無情了
That's cold. That's dead cold.

353
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:17,430
當然，要不是你年紀都這么大了 還不算太殘酷
Of course, it wouldn't be so bad if you weren't so damn old.

354
00:26:17,610 --> 00:26:20,510
嗯，至少我還能用兩只眼睛看
Yeah, well, at least I can see through both eyes.

355
00:26:21,210 --> 00:26:23,180
不過也沒給你帶來多少好處，不是嗎？
Didn't do you a lot of good though, did it?

356
00:26:24,580 --> 00:26:26,410
我還有這個訓練館
Well, I've got the gym.

357
00:26:26,580 --> 00:26:29,980
我這個年紀也不用再訓練拳手了
Don't need to be training fighters at my age.

358
00:26:31,120 --> 00:26:32,640
威利告訴你原因了？
Willie tell you why?

359
00:26:32,820 --> 00:26:35,720
是米奇 米奇有他的關系
It was Mickey. Mickey's got the connections.

360
00:26:35,890 --> 00:26:39,220
這不是因為關系 這是因為你對他沒有信心
Oh, it ain't about connections. It's about you not believing in him.

361
00:26:39,390 --> 00:26:42,090
我發掘了他 在他身上花了八年的心血
Well, I found him, I stuck with him for eight years.

362
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:43,900
這叫我對他沒信心？
How's that for not believing in him?

363
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:47,470
兩年前你就可以讓他去打冠軍賽了 他是知道的
You could've got him a title fight two years ago. Hell, he knew that.

364
00:26:47,470 --> 00:26:49,730
他能在你身邊呆這么久 我都感到吃驚
I'm amazed he stayed around this long.

365
00:26:49,730 --> 00:26:53,170
這個嘛，去參加比賽 和把腰帶贏回家完全是兩回事
Well, getting there and taking home the belt are two different things.

366
00:26:53,170 --> 00:26:56,240
我應該怎么辦 讓他去參加贏不了的比賽？
What was I supposed to do, just put him in over his head?

367
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,740
不保護他？
Not protect him?

368
00:26:57,740 --> 00:27:00,300
哦，你是在保護他不讓他拿冠軍？
Oh, you were protecting him from the championship.

369
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:03,960
- 對    - 唔，現在聽起來合情合理了
- Yeah.    - Well, now it makes sense.

370
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:07,690
那你又怎么樣呢，斯科雷普？ 你的經理當時做了什么？
Well, what about you, Scrap? What did your manager do?

371
00:27:07,690 --> 00:27:10,450
你曾經是多么優秀的拳手 比威利要棒
You were a hell of a fighter, better than Willie.

372
00:27:10,530 --> 00:27:13,560
他給了你一場冠軍賽 還是把你扔在那里...
He get you a title fight, or did he just bust you out...

373
00:27:13,560 --> 00:27:17,530
...讓對手用拳頭不停打你的頭 直到把眼睛打沒了？
...banging your head against other people's fists until you lost your eye?

374
00:27:17,530 --> 00:27:19,500
至少我有個機會
I had my shot.

375
00:27:19,500 --> 00:27:22,260
我去揮舞過我的拳頭 沒有人能說我沒努力過
I went out swinging, and no man can say I didn't.

376
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:23,660
是啊，我記得
Yeah, well, I remember.

377
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:27,590
但是請不要因為 我不想讓我的拳手下半輩子...
And excuse me if I didn't want my fighter spending the second half of his life...

378
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:31,340
- ...都在清掃別人吐在地上的口水而介意    - 嗯，是啊
...cleaning up other people's spit.    - Yeah, right.

379
00:27:31,560 --> 00:27:35,640
對，你是聰明人 你還學希臘語呢
Right, you're the smart one. You're the one learning Greek.

380
00:27:36,050 --> 00:27:37,450
是高盧語
It's Gaelic.

381
00:27:37,450 --> 00:27:40,760
你剛剛把自己參加 冠軍爭霸戰的機會保護沒了
Well, you just protected yourself out of a championship fight.

382
00:27:40,760 --> 00:27:44,120
這句話用高盧語怎么說？
How do you say that in Gaelic?

383
00:28:51,070 --> 00:28:53,660
抱歉
Sorry.

384
00:29:00,130 --> 00:29:01,860
謝謝
Thanks.

385
00:29:01,860 --> 00:29:06,170
冠軍和大個子威利 瓊斯 之間的較量繼續進行...
The action continues as the champ is battling Big Willie Jones...

386
00:29:06,170 --> 00:29:08,330
...他被冠軍用 連續的左右拳控制住了
...and commanding him with rights and lefts.

387
00:29:08,330 --> 00:29:11,670
逼到了繩圈的邊上 他在用左拳攻擊....
Up against the ropes, he's hitting him with the left...

388
00:29:11,760 --> 00:29:15,330
拳擊是一種不自然的運動
Boxing is an unnatural act.

389
00:29:15,330 --> 00:29:18,850
因為拳擊中的每樣東西都是逆向的
Because everything in it is backwards.

390
00:29:20,190 --> 00:29:22,220
你想向左移動...
You wanna move to the left...

391
00:29:22,220 --> 00:29:26,290
... 不是向左邁步 而是右腳趾用力
...you don't step left, you push on the right toe.

392
00:29:26,730 --> 00:29:30,430
向右移動的時候左腳趾用力
To move right, you use your left toe.

393
00:29:30,430 --> 00:29:34,520
你要迎著痛苦而上 而不是...
Instead of running from the pain, like a sane person would do...

394
00:29:34,520 --> 00:29:36,700
...象有理智的人那樣躲避
...you step into it.

395
00:29:37,320 --> 00:29:41,660
大個子威利反擊了，噢，天哪 他一記右手拳擊中了衛冕拳王
But Big Willie comes back. Oh, my God, he hits the champ with a right hand.

396
00:29:41,660 --> 00:29:44,250
衛冕拳王倒下了
And the champ is down.

397
00:29:44,250 --> 00:29:46,720
女士們先生們 裁判正在數點
Ladies and gentleman, the ref is in for the count.

398
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:50,250
大個子威利 瓊斯 成為了新的世界冠軍
And Big Willie Jones is the new champion of the world.

399
00:29:50,250 --> 00:29:54,050
今晚發生的一切令人難以置信...
It's unbelievable how this has taken place tonight...

400
00:29:54,050 --> 00:29:58,120
...不過朋友們，新的冠軍產生了
...but there you have it, folks, a new champion.

401
00:29:58,910 --> 00:30:02,790
拳擊中的每樣東西都是逆向的
Everything in boxing is backwards.

402
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:19,140
要芝士漢堡嗎？
Want a cheeseburger?

403
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:21,110
- 你給我買了個芝士漢堡？    - 嗯
- You bought me a cheeseburger?    - Yeah.

404
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:23,310
我從沒見你給別人買過芝士漢堡
I never see you buy anybody a cheeseburger.

405
00:30:23,310 --> 00:30:26,510
我點了，可我吃不了，你愿意吃么？
Well, I couldn't eat it, and I ordered it. You want it?

406
00:30:26,510 --> 00:30:30,380
噢，我猜地球又開始轉了
Well, I guess the planet can go back to spinning.

407
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:35,070
- 你看比賽了么？    - 嗯，看了
- You watch the fight?    - Yeah, I watched it.

408
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:37,960
威利打的不錯
Willie did good.

409
00:30:38,270 --> 00:30:40,070
這就是你要說的？
That's what you've got to say?

410
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:43,460
威利贏了，不是嗎？ 他打的不錯
Well, he won, didn't he? He did good.

411
00:30:43,670 --> 00:30:48,240
我看出你正在改變自己 學著敞開心扉，很不錯
I see you been working on yourself, learning to open up. That's good work.

412
00:30:48,240 --> 00:30:50,230
你看了？
You watch it?

413
00:30:50,230 --> 00:30:53,140
是啊，我有HBO臺
Yeah, I got HBO.

414
00:30:53,300 --> 00:30:55,800
你怎么可能看得起HBO？
Now, how can you afford HBO?

415
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:59,800
我從什么時候起就叫你省錢了？
How long have I been telling you to save your money?

416
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:02,500
從我和“臺風”路易斯 強森...
Ever since I fought Louis "Typhoon" Johnson...

417
00:31:02,500 --> 00:31:05,490
...在密西西比州圖皮洛市的 俱樂部體育館比賽以后
...at the Stadium Club in Tupelo, Mississippi.

418
00:31:05,560 --> 00:31:07,720
- 真的？    - 是的
- That true?    - Yeah.

419
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:11,560
經理人跑路了 讓我們自己搭車回家
Manager ran off and left you and me to hitch home.

420
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:13,030
你難道什么都不記得了么？
Don't you remember nothing?

421
00:31:13,030 --> 00:31:17,660
我記得走到一半的時候 覺得自己要被私刑處死了
Well, I remember walking halfway and thinking I was gonna be lynched.

422
00:31:17,660 --> 00:31:21,740
我記得你把口袋空空的我 扔在那個加油站
I remember you leaving me with my dick in my hand behind that gas station.

423
00:31:21,740 --> 00:31:25,380
是啊，我當時搭到一個便車 我一關上門那家伙就開走了
Yeah, well, I got a ride. The guy took off before I hardly closed the door.

424
00:31:25,380 --> 00:31:28,060
后來我不得不又往回走了兩英里
I had to walk back two miles.

425
00:31:28,060 --> 00:31:32,050
你的良心占了上風 這就是原因
Your conscience got the better of you, that's what.

426
00:31:34,580 --> 00:31:36,960
那他媽是什么聲音？
What the hell's that?

427
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:39,920
今天是她的生日
It's her birthday.

428
00:32:01,030 --> 00:32:05,270
你的呼吸方法不對 這就是為什么你大口喘氣
You're not breathing right. That's why you're panting.

429
00:32:05,410 --> 00:32:07,720
今天是你生日，是嗎？
So it's your birthday, huh?

430
00:32:07,720 --> 00:32:10,420
那你多大了？
How old does that make you?

431
00:32:10,420 --> 00:32:13,210
我32了，鄧先生
I'm 32, Mr.Dunn.

432
00:32:13,210 --> 00:32:16,950
我在這里慶祝 我又花了一年的時間洗盤子和當女招待
I'm celebrating that I spent another year scraping dishes and waitressing...

433
00:32:16,950 --> 00:32:19,120
我從13歲就開始干這些了
...which is what I been doing since 13.

434
00:32:19,120 --> 00:32:24,310
根據您的理論 我37歲之前打不出一記象樣的拳...
And according to you, I'll be 37 before I can even throw a decent punch...

435
00:32:24,310 --> 00:32:27,220
...打了這個梨球一個月 一點進展也沒有...
...which after working this speed bag for a month and getting nowhere...

436
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:29,590
...我現在認識到 上帝的現實也許就是這樣
...I now realize may be God's simple truth.

437
00:32:29,590 --> 00:32:31,900
另外的現實是，我的哥哥在監獄里
Other truth is, my brother's in prison...

438
00:32:31,900 --> 00:32:35,680
我的妹妹假裝 自己的一個孩子還活著，詐騙福利金
...my sister cheats on welfare by pretending one of her kids is still alive...

439
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:38,910
我爸爸死了 我媽有312磅重
...my daddy's dead, and my mama weighs 312 pounds.

440
00:32:38,950 --> 00:32:41,900
如果我還有理智的話 我應該回家去
If I was thinking straight, I'd go back home...

441
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:46,780
找個二手的活動房屋 買個炸鍋，再來點夾心餅干
...find a used trailer, buy a deep fryer and some Oreos.

442
00:32:46,780 --> 00:32:50,520
問題是，這是唯一我喜歡做的事情
The problem is, this is the only thing I ever felt good doing.

443
00:32:50,520 --> 00:32:54,100
如果對于拳擊來說我太老了 那我就一無所有
If I'm too old for this, then I got nothing.

444
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,760
這下你滿意了吧？
That enough truth to suit you?

445
00:32:58,320 --> 00:32:59,790
這是你的梨球？
This your speed bag?

446
00:32:59,790 --> 00:33:03,400
把你的放在臺子后面了 真希望能說那是我用壞的
Put yours behind the counter. Wish I could say I wore it out.

447
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:08,490
好了，停一下，停一下
Okay, just hold it. Hold it.

448
00:33:08,490 --> 00:33:11,790
我要教你幾件事情 然后給你找個訓練師
I'll show you a few things, and then we'll get you a trainer.

449
00:33:11,790 --> 00:33:13,600
不用了，抱歉
No, sorry.

450
00:33:13,600 --> 00:33:16,240
- 你還打算討價還價？    - 是的，先生
- You're in a position to negotiate?    - Yes, sir.

451
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:20,820
是的，因為我知道如果你正確的訓練我 我會成為冠軍
Because I know if you train me right, I'm gonna be a champ.

452
00:33:21,860 --> 00:33:23,700
我見過你看著我的樣子
I seen you looking at me.

453
00:33:23,700 --> 00:33:26,810
- 是的，用憐憫的眼神    - 你不要這么說
- Yeah, out of pity.    - Don't you say that.

454
00:33:26,810 --> 00:33:30,240
你不要這么說，如果不是事實的話
Don't you say that if it ain't true.

455
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:32,130
我要的是訓練師
I want a trainer.

456
00:33:32,330 --> 00:33:36,210
我不要施舍 我也不要幫忙
I don't want charity, and I don't want favors.

457
00:33:39,950 --> 00:33:43,680
如果你不感興趣，那我還要繼續慶祝
If you're not interested, then I got more celebrating to do.

458
00:33:45,540 --> 00:33:47,810
停，停，停
Stop, stop, stop.

459
00:33:47,810 --> 00:33:52,350
該死，停下來 你到底在做什么？
Goddamn it, stop. What the hell are you doing?

460
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,720
好吧
Okay.

461
00:33:58,030 --> 00:33:59,470
如果我來教你--
If I'm gonna take you on...

462
00:33:59,630 --> 00:34:03,130
- 你一定不會后悔的    - 聽我說就行了
- You won't never regret it.    - Look, just listen to me.

463
00:34:03,300 --> 00:34:06,140
- 如果我來教你--    - 我保證我會非常努力
- If I take you on...    - I promise I'll work so hard.

464
00:34:06,310 --> 00:34:08,710
天，這已經是個錯誤了
God, this is a mistake already.

465
00:34:10,680 --> 00:34:12,310
我聽著呢，老板
I'm listening, boss.

466
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:17,710
如果我來教你，你一句話也不要說 你不能對我有疑問
If I take you on, you don't say anything, you don't question me.

467
00:34:18,190 --> 00:34:21,920
不要問我問題 除了“是，弗蘭基”以外什么也不要說
You don't ask why, you don't say anything except maybe, "Yes, Frankie."

468
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:25,190
還有我會試著忘記 你是個女孩這個事實
And I'm gonna try to forget the fact that you're a girl.

469
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,590
我就要求這么多
That's all I ask.

470
00:34:26,760 --> 00:34:29,250
另外如果你受傷了別對我哭
And don't come crying to me if you get hurt.

471
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:32,020
- 好的    - 我們一言為定
- Alrighty.    - We got a deal.

472
00:34:32,470 --> 00:34:34,370
沒，還沒有
No, not quite.

473
00:34:34,540 --> 00:34:36,500
我教你怎么打拳
I'm gonna teach you how to fight...

474
00:34:36,670 --> 00:34:39,370
然后給你找個經理人 我就放手不管了
...then we'll get you a manager, and I'm off down the road.

475
00:34:39,540 --> 00:34:43,140
- 我不想和你爭，不過--    - 別跟我爭，我們就這么辦
- I hate to argue with you, but...    - Don't argue, that's the way we're doing it.

476
00:34:43,310 --> 00:34:47,080
我會教你一切你需要知道的 然后你自己去掙個一百萬美元
I teach you all you need to know, and you go off and make a million dollars.

477
00:34:47,250 --> 00:34:50,180
我不管 被人打掉牙齒，我也不管
I don't care. You get your teeth knocked out, I don't care.

478
00:34:50,350 --> 00:34:53,550
我不想聽 這個東西就是這樣
I don't wanna hear about it. That's just the way it's gonna be.

479
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:55,280
只有這樣我才同意教你
It's the only way I'll do it.

480
00:35:03,530 --> 00:35:04,690
好的
All right.

481
00:35:05,830 --> 00:35:10,790
在訓練場里我注意到一件事 你從來不移動你的腳
Now, one of the things I've noticed around the gym is you never move your feet.

482
00:35:10,970 --> 00:35:14,270
你總是呆呆的站在那里 你必須要移動你的腳
You stand there just flat-footed. You've gotta move your feet.

483
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:16,600
這是我將教會你最有用的東西之一
That's one of the best things I can teach you.

484
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:19,610
那么，你應該這么做
So here's what you do.

485
00:35:19,850 --> 00:35:22,250
把自己-- 膝蓋彎曲一點
You get yourself... Bend your knees a little bit.

486
00:35:22,750 --> 00:35:26,310
擺好運動姿態 就好像你打算要打什么一樣
Get in an athletic position. Look like you're gonna hit something.

487
00:35:28,660 --> 00:35:31,560
- 怎么做，老板？    - 就--打--梨球就行了
- Move them how, boss?    - Just... Go... Hit the bag.

488
00:35:33,430 --> 00:35:35,220
- 停    - 我做錯什么了？
- Stop.    - What'd I do wrong?

489
00:35:35,400 --> 00:35:37,560
好，你做錯了兩件事情
Okay, you did two things wrong.

490
00:35:37,730 --> 00:35:41,060
第一，你問了我一個問題 第二，你又問了一個問題
One is you asked a question, and two is you asked another question.

491
00:35:41,570 --> 00:35:45,400
現在我要你做的 不是要打得多么狠
Now, what I want you to do, it's not about hitting it hard...

492
00:35:45,570 --> 00:35:49,510
而是打得多么好 所以看著我
...it's how good you hit it. So watch me.

493
00:35:49,680 --> 00:35:51,300
如果你愿意的話可以和我一起數
You can count with me if you want.

494
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:54,310
就是數數 數一的時候，我打一下球
It's just count. On a one-count, I hit right through the bag.

495
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:56,470
- 你能再示范一次么？    - 數--
- Can you show me that again?    - I just...

496
00:35:56,650 --> 00:35:58,680
數一就行了，拜托
Just say "one," please.

497
00:35:58,850 --> 00:36:00,340
- 一    - 好
- One.    - Okay.

498
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:02,350
- 一，好    - 一
- One. Okay.    - One.

499
00:36:02,520 --> 00:36:05,650
對，就說一 很好，很好
Yeah, just say "one." That's good. That's good.

500
00:36:05,830 --> 00:36:10,490
然后我移動到我的右腳 你可以看到我的重心都轉移到右腳
Then I move over to my right foot. You'll see my weight is shifting to my right foot.

501
00:36:10,930 --> 00:36:15,870
然后我用我的手背攻擊 就象用冰錐碎冰
Then I hit it with my back of my hand, sort of like I'm chipping ice with an ice pick.

502
00:36:16,040 --> 00:36:21,410
然后我轉過來，轉移到我的左腳 然后用右手攻擊
Then I come over, and I shift to my left foot, and I hit it with my right hand.

503
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:24,140
還是冰錐的動作
And ice pick maneuver again.

504
00:36:24,310 --> 00:36:27,370
再轉到右腳上 再攻擊右側
And I come over on my right foot and hit it right.

505
00:36:28,950 --> 00:36:31,680
就看著我的腳步
Don't watch anything but my feet.

506
00:36:43,130 --> 00:36:46,620
就這么做 不停練習
Just do it like that. Just keep practicing.

507
00:37:16,730 --> 00:37:20,560
你示范他們怎么站立 雙腳和肩膀平行
You show them how to stand, keep their legs under their shoulders.

508
00:37:28,980 --> 00:37:32,640
訓練一名拳手 你必須在精神上把他們剝光
To make a fighter, you gotta strip them down to bare wood.

509
00:37:32,810 --> 00:37:34,300
死了再休息
Rest when you're dead.

510
00:37:34,480 --> 00:37:36,140
過來
Come here.

511
00:37:40,650 --> 00:37:43,320
你不能只是 叫他們忘記以前知道的事情...
You can't just tell them to forget everything you know...

512
00:37:43,490 --> 00:37:46,550
... 你要叫他們從骨子里忘記
...you gotta make them forget it in their bones.

513
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:52,900
讓他們疲憊到只聽你的話
Make them so tired they only listen to you.

514
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:57,130
只能聽見你的聲音 只做你叫他們做的事情，不做其他事
Only hear your voice, only do what you say, and nothing else.

515
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:58,530
腳步移動
Move your feet.

516
00:37:58,710 --> 00:38:00,700
腳步移動起來 移動起來讓我看
Move your feet around. Let's see you go.

517
00:38:15,460 --> 00:38:18,950
教他們怎么保持平衡 怎么讓對手失去平衡
Show them how to keep their balance and take it away from the other guy.

518
00:38:19,130 --> 00:38:22,860
別這么低，看著我 右勾拳，然后向右
Not so low. Look at me. Right hook and just turn right.

519
00:38:27,230 --> 00:38:29,960
如何用右腳趾產生動力
How to generate momentum off your right toe.

520
00:38:31,670 --> 00:38:34,470
出刺拳時如何彎曲膝蓋
And how to flex your knees when you fire a jab.

521
00:38:40,750 --> 00:38:45,010
如何在后退中攻擊 好讓對手在追擊你時有所顧忌
How to fight backing up, so that the other guy doesn't wanna come after you.

522
00:38:45,590 --> 00:38:47,820
然后你要再全部教他們一遍
Then you gotta show them all over again.

523
00:38:47,990 --> 00:38:50,180
一遍又一遍...
Over and over and over...

524
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:53,330
...直到他們感覺一切與生俱來
...till they think they were born that way.

525
00:38:55,100 --> 00:38:56,360
轉移
Shift.

526
00:38:56,530 --> 00:38:58,430
轉移位置
Shift away.

527
00:38:59,470 --> 00:39:02,630
好了，今天就到這里
Okay. That's enough for today.

528
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:06,240
不錯，好姑娘
Good work. Good girl.

529
00:39:07,540 --> 00:39:10,200
老板，你覺得我可以打比賽了么？
You think I ready for a fight, boss?

530
00:39:32,730 --> 00:39:36,170
嘿，你過來
Hey. Hey, come here.

531
00:39:38,970 --> 00:39:40,200
你都喘不過氣了
You're not breathing.

532
00:39:41,840 --> 00:39:43,570
不想和你爭論
Hate to disagree with you.

533
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:47,010
你一有壓力就喜歡屏住呼吸
Every time you get under pressure, you're holding your breath.

534
00:39:47,180 --> 00:39:50,620
- 從現在開始別這么做    - 好的
- Now, stop doing that.    - Okay.

535
00:39:50,780 --> 00:39:53,080
除了這一點，我做得很好，是吧？
But other than that, I'm doing pretty good, right?

536
00:39:53,620 --> 00:39:57,150
- 我是說，對于女孩來講    - 我不訓練女孩
- I mean, for a girl.    - I don't train girls.

537
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:02,120
老板，你覺得我可以參加比賽了么
Think I might be ready for a fight, boss?

538
00:40:02,300 --> 00:40:05,820
嗯，我們先找個經理人 然后我們再看看，好嗎？
Well, we'll get a manager, and we'll find out, won't we?

539
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:09,030
我是想找一個 可是你一直讓我抽不出時間來
I'd like to, but you been keeping me too busy.

540
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:18,670
- 有家人嗎，老板？    - 什么？
- Got any family, boss?    - What?

541
00:40:21,280 --> 00:40:24,610
我看你把所有的時間都花在我的身上了 我不知道你有沒有家人
You been spending all this time with me, I didn't know if you had any.

542
00:40:25,590 --> 00:40:26,850
沒有
No.

543
00:40:28,560 --> 00:40:30,890
呃，我是有個女兒，叫凱蒂
Well, I've got a daughter, Katy.

544
00:40:31,690 --> 00:40:32,920
她就是家人啊
That's family.

545
00:40:33,690 --> 00:40:35,790
但是我們并不那么親近
We're not exactly close.

546
00:40:36,230 --> 00:40:37,700
她多重？
How much she weigh?

547
00:40:38,970 --> 00:40:40,260
什么？
What?

548
00:40:40,430 --> 00:40:43,630
我的家庭問題和體重成正比
Trouble in my family comes by the pound.

549
00:40:45,940 --> 00:40:47,600
是嗎
Yeah.

550
00:40:47,870 --> 00:40:49,970
不是很重
Not very big.

551
00:40:50,240 --> 00:40:54,240
曾經很愛運動 不知道現在還有沒有堅持
Used to be real athletic. Don't know if she kept it up.

552
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:03,810
那么，你怎么想？
So, what do you think?

553
00:41:03,990 --> 00:41:05,890
我可以參加比賽了么？
I ready for a fight?

554
00:41:11,630 --> 00:41:13,460
嘿，賽利
Hey, Sally.

555
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:16,590
過來一下，好嗎？
Come here for a minute, will you?

556
00:41:18,010 --> 00:41:21,300
弗蘭基，能不能到后面來跟我談談？
Frankie, I need to see you in the back for a minute, okay?

557
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:24,960
- 我能和你說句話么？    - 賽利是個很優秀的經理人
- Can I see you a minute?    - Sally here's a real good manager.

558
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:29,100
他手下還有幾個拿過金手套的選手 想要女孩嗎，賽利？
Has a couple of Golden Glove boys. Looking for a girl, Sally?

559
00:41:29,100 --> 00:41:31,500
如果有優秀人選的話
I'm looking for a good one.

560
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:34,920
看，這不就有了
Well, see, there you go.

561
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:39,450
很高興和你合作，小姐
Nice working with you, girlie.

562
00:41:42,890 --> 00:41:45,330
- 你有什么事？    - 沒什么，沒什么
- What'd you want?    - Nothing. It's nothing.

563
00:41:45,330 --> 00:41:49,870
我沒撒謊，我已經看過你訓練了 你的左拳很厲害
I ain't lying, I've been watching you work. You got a hell of a left.

564
00:41:49,870 --> 00:41:51,770
謝謝你
Thank you.

565
00:41:53,180 --> 00:41:57,370
那你要不要試試？ 看看是不是合適？
So you wanna give this a try? See if it's a fit?

566
00:41:59,020 --> 00:42:02,360
- 噢，當然    - 好
- Yeah, sure.    - Good.

567
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:05,370
好，因為我覺得你已經夠資格比賽了
Because I think you're ready for a fight.

568
00:42:17,080 --> 00:42:19,090
分開
Break.

569
00:42:19,890 --> 00:42:23,130
我到底做錯了什么，賽利？ 每次我逼近都被她痛擊
What am I doing wrong, Sally? Every time I get inside, she's on me.

570
00:42:23,130 --> 00:42:26,000
你做得很好 你就快把她拖垮了，繼續出拳
You're doing great. You're wearing her down. Keep punching.

571
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:29,810
- 我不好，我要輸了    - 你就快把她拖垮了
- I ain't doing great, I'm losing.    - You're wearing her down.

572
00:42:30,980 --> 00:42:33,310
沒事吧，親愛的？看得清嗎？
You okay, honey? Can you see okay?

573
00:42:34,320 --> 00:42:36,910
- 加油    - 加油
- Come on.    - Do it.

574
00:42:37,580 --> 00:42:39,610
加油，加油！
Come on, let's do this!

575
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:45,050
沒錯！
That's it!

576
00:42:52,700 --> 00:42:54,100
今晚真不錯，不是嗎？
Nice night, eh?

577
00:42:54,500 --> 00:42:57,200
老天
Jesus Christ.

578
00:42:57,370 --> 00:42:59,240
那姑娘是羅尼 華盛頓的拳手
That's Lonnie Washington's girl.

579
00:42:59,610 --> 00:43:01,200
非常優秀的拳手
Hell of a fighter.

580
00:43:01,370 --> 00:43:03,430
11場全勝
11-0.

581
00:43:03,610 --> 00:43:05,580
左拳，左拳舉起來
Your left. Keep your left up.

582
00:43:10,350 --> 00:43:12,440
羅尼旗下有很多優秀拳手
Lonnie's got a lot of good fighters.

583
00:43:12,620 --> 00:43:15,750
輕量級冠軍喬伊 阿達喬也在他旗下
He's got Joey Adagio, lightweight champ?

584
00:43:15,920 --> 00:43:17,410
對
Yeah.

585
00:43:17,790 --> 00:43:19,620
你的左拳，該死
Your left, damn it.

586
00:43:20,530 --> 00:43:25,190
要是我肯定不會選她做第一個對手 不過賽利是個好經理人
Wouldn't have been my choice for her first fight, but Sally's a good manager.

587
00:43:25,370 --> 00:43:28,100
- 他一定認為她能打敗她    - 天哪
- He must think she can take her.    - Jesus H.

588
00:43:28,270 --> 00:43:30,900
左拳，左拳舉起來
Your left. Keep your left up.

589
00:43:31,340 --> 00:43:34,330
你認為這么遠的地方她能聽見？
You think she can hear you from back here?

590
00:43:41,380 --> 00:43:45,150
當然，就算麥琪輸了 對賽利也算不了什么
Of course, if Maggie loses, it wouldn't mean anything to Sally.

591
00:43:45,320 --> 00:43:47,310
也許還對他有幫助
Might even help him.

592
00:43:47,490 --> 00:43:49,390
讓羅尼的女選手再勝一場...
Lonnie's girl gets another win...

593
00:43:49,560 --> 00:43:54,120
...羅尼也許會讓賽利的輕量級拳手 去挑戰喬伊 阿達喬的冠軍
...Lonnie might let Sally's lightweight fight Joey Adagio for the title.

594
00:43:54,390 --> 00:43:56,730
賽利想要安排一場和阿達喬的比賽？
Sally's trying to set a fight with Adagio?

595
00:43:56,900 --> 00:43:58,330
嘿，我知道什么？
Hey, what do I know?

596
00:43:58,500 --> 00:44:01,230
我只是來欣賞比賽
I just come because I enjoy the fights.

597
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:03,960
上帝
Mother of God.

598
00:44:04,840 --> 00:44:06,330
好了，分開
Okay, break.

599
00:44:06,510 --> 00:44:08,870
嘿，過來，過來
Hey. Come here, come here.

600
00:44:09,040 --> 00:44:10,440
嘿，過來
Hey. Get over here.

601
00:44:10,610 --> 00:44:13,440
你老是放低左拳 別再放低左拳了
You're dropping your left hand. Quit dropping your left hand.

602
00:44:13,610 --> 00:44:16,340
嘿，弗蘭基 你能不能讓我跟我的拳手談談？
Hey, Frankie, you mind if I talk to my fighter?

603
00:44:16,520 --> 00:44:19,920
你干得還真不賴啊 你也是這樣指導你的輕量級選手的？
You're doing a hell of a job. Is this the way you advise your lightweight?

604
00:44:20,420 --> 00:44:22,010
我是鄧
Dunn.

605
00:44:22,190 --> 00:44:24,680
- 你在干什么？    - 我在說話，你在干什么？
- What are you doing?    - I'm talking. What are you doing?

606
00:44:24,860 --> 00:44:26,760
- 這是你的拳手么？    - 是我的拳手
- Is this your fighter?    - It's my fighter.

607
00:44:28,090 --> 00:44:30,320
真的不是那么合適，賽利
It ain't fitting real well, Sally.

608
00:44:30,500 --> 00:44:33,630
好吧，你來帶她 反正她也屁都不會打
Fine, you take her. She can't fight worth a shit anyway.

609
00:44:33,800 --> 00:44:38,200
- 誰告訴我到底怎么回事    - 我遲到了，賽利剛才只是替我
- Somebody tell me what's going on.    - I was late. Sally was just subbing for me.

610
00:44:38,370 --> 00:44:40,810
你說她是你的拳手？
You telling me this is your fighter?

611
00:44:43,010 --> 00:44:45,380
對，是我的拳手
Yeah, this is my fighter.

612
00:44:45,550 --> 00:44:47,240
那么你有10秒的時間
Then you got 10 seconds.

613
00:44:47,510 --> 00:44:50,710
我把左手舉起來了 可當我出拳的時候，就總是會放下去
I keep holding my left up, then I throw a punch and it keeps dropping.

614
00:44:50,880 --> 00:44:52,940
- 那就放下去好了    - 那就簡單多了
- Well, let it drop.    - That'd be a lot easier.

615
00:44:53,120 --> 00:44:54,280
她認為她摸透你了
She thinks she knows you.

616
00:44:54,450 --> 00:44:57,480
你左手每次放下 她就從上面打過來
Every time you drop it, she comes right over the top.

617
00:44:57,660 --> 00:45:00,890
那你就等著她，明白嗎？ 她腦子里就這么多東西
So you just wait for her, see? That's all she's thinking about.

618
00:45:01,060 --> 00:45:04,050
- 她收回右拳準備出擊的時--你聽見了嗎?    - 我聽著呢，老板
- When she cocks that right hand... You hear?    - I hear you, boss.

619
00:45:04,230 --> 00:45:07,220
如果她那么做，你就向旁邊躲一步 然后給她一記再見勾拳
When she does, step to the side and come with a good-night hook.

620
00:45:07,400 --> 00:45:08,730
- 能行嗎？    - 看我的吧
- Got one?    - Got it right here.

621
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:11,660
- 好    - 開始吧，我等著呢
- Okay.    - Fight, or I'm calling it.

622
00:45:11,840 --> 00:45:14,830
- 去教訓她吧    - 拳手的身體了解拳手自己所不了解的東西
- Go give it to her.    - The body knows what fighters don 't.

623
00:45:15,010 --> 00:45:16,240
如何保護自己
How to protect itself.

624
00:45:16,910 --> 00:45:19,210
脖子只能轉動那么多
A neck can only twist so far.

625
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:22,580
哪怕再多轉一毫米 身體就會說：
Twist it just a hair more, and the body says:

626
00:45:22,750 --> 00:45:26,910
“嘿，還是讓我來吧 因為很明顯你不知道你自己在做什么”
"Hey, I'll take it from here because you obviously don't know what you're doing."

627
00:45:27,090 --> 00:45:28,920
到中立區去
Neutral corner.

628
00:45:30,390 --> 00:45:32,260
- 看見她怎么出拳了么？    - 嗯
- See the way she did that?    - Yeah.

629
00:45:32,430 --> 00:45:35,390
舒格 雷就會這么做 這女人好象他一樣
Sugar Ray would do that. Girl's got sugar.

630
00:45:35,560 --> 00:45:41,190
“躺下，休息 等你恢復知覺我們再談”
"Lie down, now, rest, and we'll talk about this when you regain your senses."

631
00:45:41,370 --> 00:45:43,600
這個叫做擊倒心理
It's called the knockout mechanism.

632
00:45:43,770 --> 00:45:47,470
現在放松一點 你干得不錯
Don't get all carried away, now. You did good.

633
00:45:47,640 --> 00:45:49,580
謝了，老板
Thanks, boss.

634
00:45:49,980 --> 00:45:52,310
你....你忘了規矩
You... You forgot the rule.

635
00:45:52,480 --> 00:45:54,910
- 告訴我規矩是什么？    - 左手要抬起？
- Now, what is the rule?    - Keep my left up?

636
00:45:55,080 --> 00:45:58,050
規矩是要隨時保護自己
It's to protect yourself at all times.

637
00:45:58,620 --> 00:46:00,180
好，規矩是什么？
Now, what is the rule?

638
00:46:00,350 --> 00:46:03,690
- 隨時保護我自己    - 很好，很好
- Protect myself at all times.    - Good, good.

639
00:46:03,860 --> 00:46:06,090
你放棄了我 那對我是什么樣的保護？
You gave me away. How was that protecting me?

640
00:46:07,690 --> 00:46:08,920
那不是保護
It wasn't.

641
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:11,550
沒關系了
It's okay.

642
00:46:12,300 --> 00:46:16,100
- 我會練習我的左手的，老板    - 把水喝了
- I'll work on my left, boss.    - Drink your water.

643
00:46:17,200 --> 00:46:18,900
除了這一點，我怎么樣？
Other than that, how'd I do?

644
00:46:19,340 --> 00:46:22,210
很好，你做得很好
Fine. You did fine.

645
00:46:23,180 --> 00:46:24,700
你還會再放棄我么？
You gonna leave me again?

646
00:46:26,880 --> 00:46:28,540
永遠不會
Never.

647
00:46:28,720 --> 00:46:33,080
你工作的那個地方 有沒有手工制檸檬酥皮派？
That place you work, do they have homemade lemon meringue pie there?

648
00:46:33,620 --> 00:46:36,250
- 當然有    - 不是罐裝餡料的那種垃圾
- Sure.    - Not the kind with the canned-filling crap?

649
00:46:36,420 --> 00:46:40,120
噢，是很大罐的那種 標簽上寫著“手工制作”
Oh, big can, yay size. Says "homemade" on the label.

650
00:46:42,600 --> 00:46:45,620
- 我想你這個周末休息一下    - 這才星期四
- I want you to take the weekend off.    - It's only Thursday.

651
00:46:46,870 --> 00:46:50,500
- 你打算要和我爭？    - 我知道最好不要有這個想法，老板
- You gonna argue with me?    - Know better than to do that, boss.

652
00:46:51,100 --> 00:46:52,900
嗯，很好
Well, good.

653
00:46:53,070 --> 00:46:55,740
某種角度來看，拳手大都很頑固
All fighters are pigheaded some way or other.

654
00:46:56,210 --> 00:46:59,610
他們的某個部分總覺得 在某件事情上自己比別人知道的更多
Some part of them always thinks they know better than you about something.

655
00:46:59,780 --> 00:47:04,050
你能不能花幾分鐘講講圣母懷胎？
Can you spare a few minutes for the Immaculate Conception?

656
00:47:05,650 --> 00:47:09,520
實際上，就算他們錯了...
Truth is, even if they're wrong...

657
00:47:09,690 --> 00:47:12,680
...就算有那么件事情 可以把他們都毀了...
...even if that one thing is gonna be the ruin of them...

658
00:47:12,860 --> 00:47:17,690
...如果你能把他們徹底打敗 那他們就不算是拳手了
...if you can beat that last bit out of them, then they ain 't fighters at all.

659
00:47:17,860 --> 00:47:21,130
- 我記得我說過讓你周一再來    - 沒錯，老板
- Thought I said I'd see you Monday.    - You sure did, boss.

660
00:47:21,770 --> 00:47:23,030
就是昨晚說的
That was last night.

661
00:47:23,200 --> 00:47:26,000
你說不要和你爭論
You said not to argue with you.

662
00:47:37,420 --> 00:47:40,110
該死的女人總是不按我的指揮做事
Damn woman won't do a thing I tell her.

663
00:47:40,290 --> 00:47:42,250
想聽我的建議么？
You want my advice?

664
00:47:42,420 --> 00:47:43,890
什么？
What?

665
00:47:44,820 --> 00:47:46,310
你的鞋子哪去了？
Where are your shoes?

666
00:47:47,660 --> 00:47:49,690
我給我的腳透透風
I'm airing out my feet.

667
00:47:51,430 --> 00:47:53,300
你的襪子上凈是大洞
You got big holes in your socks.

668
00:47:54,330 --> 00:47:56,330
噢，沒有那么大啦
Oh, they're not that big.

669
00:47:58,100 --> 00:48:00,370
我不是給你錢去買新的了嗎？
Didn't I give you money for some new ones?

670
00:48:02,010 --> 00:48:03,700
這是我的睡襪
These are my sleeping socks.

671
00:48:05,080 --> 00:48:07,740
我的腳晚上需要一些新鮮空氣
My feet like a little air at night.

672
00:48:08,310 --> 00:48:10,580
那你為什么要在白天穿它們？
How come you're wearing them in the daytime, then?

673
00:48:10,750 --> 00:48:13,740
因為我白天穿的襪子上洞太多了
Because my daytime socks got too many holes in them.

674
00:48:16,020 --> 00:48:21,590
那好，如果我多給你些錢 你能去買幾雙新的么？
Well, if I give you some more money, you buy some new socks.

675
00:48:21,930 --> 00:48:23,560
拜托？
Please?

676
00:48:25,930 --> 00:48:29,770
嗯，很有吸引力 不過我不能保證
Well, I'd be tempted, but I couldn't say for sure.

677
00:48:29,940 --> 00:48:31,870
也許會跑到跑道上去
Might find its way to the track.

678
00:48:48,390 --> 00:48:51,620
比賽結束，比賽結束
It's over. It's over.

679
00:49:06,440 --> 00:49:09,140
麥琪沒花多少時間就取得連勝
Didn't take Maggie long to hit her stride.

680
00:49:20,590 --> 00:49:22,020
我解決了呼吸的問題.
I got the breathing thing down.

681
00:49:22,190 --> 00:49:25,750
不，你還是呼吸不正確 因為你第一回合就把對方打倒了
No, you ain't breathing because you're knocking them out in the first round.

682
00:49:25,930 --> 00:49:29,450
- 我還以為那就是重點    - 重點是讓自己變強
- Thought that was the point.    - The point is to get good.

683
00:49:30,100 --> 00:49:32,690
把對方第一回合就擊倒 自己怎么可能進步
Can't get good if you keep knocking them out first round.

684
00:49:32,870 --> 00:49:35,060
我怎么給你再找到對手？
How am I gonna get you fights?

685
00:49:36,840 --> 00:49:39,170
沒人愿意自己的拳手被羞辱
Nobody wants to see their fighter embarrassed, now.

686
00:49:39,340 --> 00:49:41,970
為什么我還要 打這種四回合比賽，老板？
Why am I still doing four-rounders, boss?

687
00:49:42,510 --> 00:49:44,740
因為你的肺還打不了六回合
Because you haven't got the lungs for six rounds.

688
00:49:44,910 --> 00:49:48,110
我一直這么在第一回合 就把她們擊倒就行了
I do if I keep knocking them out in the first round.

689
00:49:52,050 --> 00:49:55,280
弗蘭基讓她又打了場四回合比賽...
Frankie made her fight one more four-rounder...

690
00:49:55,460 --> 00:49:57,650
...只是讓她明白誰說了算數
...just to let her know who was boss.

691
00:50:01,690 --> 00:50:04,690
三，四，五...
Three, four, five...

692
00:50:04,860 --> 00:50:06,700
...六，七....
...six, seven...

693
00:50:06,700 --> 00:50:08,760
抱歉，老板
Sorry, boss.

694
00:50:08,940 --> 00:50:10,990
麥琪對此毫不懷疑
Maggie left no doubt about it.

695
00:50:19,400 --> 00:50:23,140
好了，加油
All right, let's do it.

696
00:50:23,770 --> 00:50:28,280
但是第一場六回合賽并沒那么輕松
Her first six-rounder didn't go quite as smooth.

697
00:50:42,500 --> 00:50:44,860
起來！
Get up!

698
00:50:44,860 --> 00:50:46,330
到你的角落去
To your corner.

699
00:50:46,330 --> 00:50:49,660
- 三，四，五...    - 起來
- Three, four, five...    - Get up.

700
00:50:49,660 --> 00:50:52,060
- ...六，七...    - 起來
...six, seven...    - Get up.

701
00:50:52,060 --> 00:50:55,670
- ...八，九，十，比賽結束    - 你能做到
...eight, nine, ten. It's over.    - You can do this.

702
00:50:56,390 --> 00:51:00,990
麥琪到了第一回合結尾才將對方擊倒
Maggie didn't knock her out till the end of the first round.

703
00:51:00,990 --> 00:51:05,720
在那以后，沒有經理愿意 讓自己的拳手和麥琪交手
After that, no manager wanted to put his fighter in with Maggie.

704
00:51:09,190 --> 00:51:12,420
弗蘭基不得不自己討腰包 來給她安排比賽...
Frankie had to go into his pocket to get her decent fights...

705
00:51:12,420 --> 00:51:17,030
...靠給對方經理人賄賂 來增加對方參賽的興趣
...sweetening the purse by paying managers on the side.

706
00:51:28,450 --> 00:51:31,080
這并沒能持續太久
That only worked for so long.

707
00:51:31,080 --> 00:51:34,390
然后弗蘭基做了他不愿意做的事
Then Frankie did something he hated doing.

708
00:51:34,390 --> 00:51:36,050
他冒了次險
He took a chance.

709
00:51:38,180 --> 00:51:40,550
開始
Box.

710
00:51:44,280 --> 00:51:46,950
他把她晉升了一個級別
He moved her up in class.

711
00:51:46,950 --> 00:51:50,430
這差點成為一個錯誤
That could've been a mistake.

712
00:52:02,670 --> 00:52:04,720
注意右邊！
Watch the right!

713
00:52:06,440 --> 00:52:09,280
注意，注意
Watch it. Watch it.

714
00:52:15,540 --> 00:52:20,060
分開，分開，后退，時間到
Break, break. Step back. Break. Time.

715
00:52:27,990 --> 00:52:31,110
該死，該死，該死
Damn, damn, damn.

716
00:52:32,930 --> 00:52:34,560
給我們兩秒鐘，好嗎？
Give us two seconds, will you?

717
00:52:34,560 --> 00:52:36,940
- 好    - 兩秒鐘就好
- Okay.    - Just two seconds.

718
00:52:37,100 --> 00:52:39,500
- 你的鼻梁骨斷了    - 噢，該死
- Your nose is broke.    - Oh, damn.

719
00:52:39,500 --> 00:52:41,440
- 弄好它    - 我沒辦法，我沒辦法
- Fix it.    - I can't, I can't.

720
00:52:41,440 --> 00:52:44,140
- 你可以的    - 我不行，我準備棄權了
- You can fix it.    - I can't. I've gotta call it.

721
00:52:44,140 --> 00:52:46,410
我見你做過，弄好它
I've seen what you can do. Fix it.

722
00:52:46,410 --> 00:52:49,410
我能把它按回去 但是我不能給你止血
I can snap it back into place, but I can't stop the bleeding.

723
00:52:49,410 --> 00:52:51,110
醫務裁判會中止比賽的
The ring doctor's gonna call it.

724
00:52:51,110 --> 00:52:55,030
求你，弗蘭基，你要是能幫我止血 我就能打倒她
Please, Frankie, if you can stop the blood, I can beat her.

725
00:52:55,810 --> 00:52:58,370
咬住這個
Bite down on this.

726
00:53:15,910 --> 00:53:17,540
- 吸氣    - 什么？
- Inhale.    - What?

727
00:53:17,540 --> 00:53:19,410
- 吸氣    - 什么
- Inhale.    - What?

728
00:53:19,410 --> 00:53:21,750
吸氣
Breathe in.

729
00:53:32,360 --> 00:53:35,330
- 可以？    - 嗯，沒問題
- Okay, huh?    - Yeah, it's okay.

730
00:53:35,330 --> 00:53:38,600
好，這個變成噴泉之前你有20秒鐘...
All right, you got 20 seconds before this turns into a geyser...

731
00:53:38,600 --> 00:53:40,910
...血會噴到整個前排座位上的
...and it's gonna spray all over the front row.

732
00:53:40,910 --> 00:53:43,270
你只有20秒
Twenty seconds, that's all you've got.

733
00:53:43,270 --> 00:53:45,650
去吧
Now get going.

734
00:53:57,760 --> 00:54:00,230
回到你的角落去
Go to your corner.

735
00:54:00,760 --> 00:54:03,700
三，四，五...
Three, four, five...

736
00:54:03,700 --> 00:54:07,570
- 加油，呼吸，呼吸    - ...六，七，八...
- Come on, breathe. Breathe. ...six, seven, eight...

737
00:54:07,570 --> 00:54:10,300
...九，十
...nine, ten.

738
00:54:13,070 --> 00:54:15,200
“莫 庫什勒”
Mo cuishle.

739
00:54:20,150 --> 00:54:22,480
- 好！    - 太棒了！
- All right!    - Yeah!

740
00:54:23,720 --> 00:54:25,760
對
Right.

741
00:54:29,360 --> 00:54:31,730
你在讀什么
What you reading?

742
00:54:32,030 --> 00:54:33,860
她說什么？
What's she saying?

743
00:54:33,860 --> 00:54:36,400
想知道你在讀什么
Wants to know what you're reading.

744
00:54:36,400 --> 00:54:39,870
是葉芝的作品（愛爾蘭著名詩人） 仰著點頭
It's Yeats. Keep your head back.

745
00:54:40,140 --> 00:54:42,270
你為什么不跟她說說葉芝呢？
Why don't you talk a little Yeats to her.

746
00:54:42,270 --> 00:54:45,480
告訴她那是怎樣一件樂事
Show her what a treat that is.

747
00:54:45,480 --> 00:54:47,610
他媽的什么時候才能輪到她？
When the hell they gonna get to her?

748
00:54:47,610 --> 00:54:50,510
我很好，弗蘭基
I'm okay, Frankie.

749
00:54:50,620 --> 00:54:53,750
- 你今天學到了什么？    - 隨時保護自己
- What'd you learn tonight?    - Always protect myself.

750
00:54:53,750 --> 00:54:57,030
- 規矩是什么？    - 隨時保護自己
- What's the rule?    - Always protect myself.

751
00:54:57,030 --> 00:54:59,520
- 麥琪 菲斯杰拉德?    - 在這里
- Margaret Fitzgerald?    - Here.

752
00:55:03,430 --> 00:55:06,030
我就在這兒等你
I'll be right here.

753
00:55:17,350 --> 00:55:19,990
- 你怎么樣？    - 我？
- How you doing?    - Me?

754
00:55:19,990 --> 00:55:22,580
- 對，你    - 我又沒有受傷
- Yeah, you.    - I'm not the one who's hurt.

755
00:55:26,830 --> 00:55:29,250
鼻子斷了并不是那么受傷
Broken nose don't hurt that much.

756
00:55:29,390 --> 00:55:32,290
為什么你要告訴我這個？
Why are you telling me that?

757
00:55:33,860 --> 00:55:35,360
沒有原因
No reason.

758
00:55:35,360 --> 00:55:39,910
可有些傷太深了 或是離骨頭太近
But some wounds are too deep or too close to the bone.

759
00:55:39,910 --> 00:55:44,580
不管你如何努力，都不能止血
And no matter how hard you work at it, you just can't stop the bleeding.

760
00:55:44,580 --> 00:55:48,570
- 你給你女兒寫信了么？    - 每周都寫
- Did you write your daughter?    - Every week.

761
00:55:49,480 --> 00:55:53,100
我真不明白你為什么要來教堂
I've no idea why you come to church.

762
00:56:23,690 --> 00:56:29,010
在連續十二場比賽擊倒對手勝出后 弗蘭基得到幾個非常不錯的邀請
After her 12th straight knockout, Frankie got a couple of real good offers.

763
00:56:30,970 --> 00:56:33,740
第一個邀請是和 “蘭熊”比麗 奧斯特曼...
The first was to fight Billie "The Blue Bear" Osterman...

764
00:56:33,740 --> 00:56:36,720
...爭奪WBA次中量級頭銜
...for the WBA welterweight title.

765
00:56:38,050 --> 00:56:40,010
“蘭熊”比麗
Billie "The Blue Bear."

766
00:56:40,010 --> 00:56:43,310
比麗原來是東柏林的妓女
Billie was a former prostitute out of East Berlin.

767
00:56:43,310 --> 00:56:48,130
她是這個級別里 手法最骯臟的拳手，臭名遠揚
Had a reputation for being the dirtiest fighter in the ranks.

768
00:57:05,940 --> 00:57:07,540
她看起來一點也不在乎...
Didn't seem to matter to her...

769
00:57:07,540 --> 00:57:10,780
...這樣的動作可能會致人于死地
...that something like that could kill a person.

770
00:57:11,080 --> 00:57:13,890
觀眾喜歡她
And the crowds loved her.

771
00:57:16,220 --> 00:57:19,350
他沒告訴她就把這場比賽拒絕了.
He turned it down without even telling her.

772
00:57:19,350 --> 00:57:21,780
下一個邀請是去挑戰英國冠軍
The next was to fight the British champ...

773
00:57:21,780 --> 00:57:25,700
- 一個剛被比麗擊敗的牙買加女孩    - 喂？
- ...a Jamaican girl Billie just beat.    - Hello?

774
00:57:25,880 --> 00:57:28,500
不感興趣
Not interested.

775
00:57:30,710 --> 00:57:33,900
他也沒接受那個邀請
He turned that down too.

776
00:57:35,430 --> 00:57:37,890
可是很大一筆錢哪，老板
That's a lot of money, boss.

777
00:57:37,890 --> 00:57:41,520
是啊，你掙錢了 為什么還在這里工作？
Yeah, you're making money. What are you still working here for?

778
00:57:41,520 --> 00:57:43,390
那是冠軍賽，對吧？
It's a title match, right?

779
00:57:43,390 --> 00:57:46,540
你是英國人么？ 那個冠軍你拿不走的
Are you British? It's a title you can't take away.

780
00:57:46,540 --> 00:57:50,560
她沒什么好輸的 你也沒什么好贏的
She's got nothing to lose, you got nothing to win.

781
00:57:50,670 --> 00:57:53,400
很可能仍然是一場不錯的比賽呢
Might still be a good fight.

782
00:57:53,400 --> 00:57:57,100
是啊，我剛把你升上次中量級
Yeah, I just... I just brought you up to welterweight.

783
00:57:57,100 --> 00:58:00,720
能和跟你水平相當的選手打就不錯了 還想他媽去挑戰那些冠軍？
Too good to fight these contenders, you'd rather fight some bullshit champ?

784
00:58:00,720 --> 00:58:04,410
我沒發現有和我水平相當的選手啊
Didn't notice I was fighting any contenders.

785
00:58:04,520 --> 00:58:08,410
如果你想的話 隨時可以換經理
Well, you can get yourself another manager any time you want.

786
00:58:08,780 --> 00:58:11,840
實際上，如果你有能力 把自己的臉保護得好一點的話...
In fact, if you'd learn to protect your face a little better...

787
00:58:11,840 --> 00:58:15,110
...我才不會拒絕這筆錢呢
...I wouldn't have to turn down this money.

788
00:58:17,700 --> 00:58:22,020
我的臉暴露出那么多 可還沒被擊倒過，真是個奇跡
My face is out there so much it's a miracle I haven't been knocked out yet.

789
00:58:51,990 --> 00:58:53,860
你今晚不要繼續訓練了
No, you can't work here anymore tonight.

790
00:58:54,890 --> 00:58:56,690
我定了位子
I made us a reservation.

791
00:58:58,030 --> 00:59:02,690
你去洗個澡吧
You might wanna shower.

792
00:59:21,850 --> 00:59:24,010
你的
Here you go.

793
00:59:24,190 --> 00:59:26,050
你的
Here you go.

794
00:59:26,560 --> 00:59:28,250
這是什么？
What's this?

795
00:59:28,430 --> 00:59:31,720
你想要的東西 這不是什么秘密
Well, it ain't no big secret what you're wishing for.

796
00:59:32,260 --> 00:59:33,730
把蠟燭吹了
Go on and blow.

797
00:59:38,640 --> 00:59:40,360
謝謝你
Thank you.

798
00:59:44,470 --> 00:59:46,970
33歲不算大的
Thirty-three ain't so old.

799
00:59:47,710 --> 00:59:50,540
我39歲的時候還在參賽
I was still fighting at 39.

800
00:59:51,850 --> 00:59:54,370
我打了23年
Fought for 23 years.

801
00:59:58,120 --> 00:59:59,780
最近怎么樣，斯科雷普
How's it going, Scrap?

802
00:59:59,960 --> 01:00:01,620
不錯，米奇
Doing good, Mickey.

803
01:00:02,690 --> 01:00:04,490
不錯
Doing good.

804
01:00:05,900 --> 01:00:08,420
- 你要什么？    - 咖啡
- What'll you have?    - Coffee.

805
01:00:13,940 --> 01:00:16,200
你們兩個不講話？
You two not speaking?

806
01:00:16,640 --> 01:00:18,870
不太認識他
Don't hardly know him.

807
01:00:23,810 --> 01:00:28,010
我在37歲生日之后遇到了弗蘭基
I met Frankie right after my 37th birthday.

808
01:00:29,050 --> 01:00:31,610
那時他干的工作是給拳手包扎傷口
He was picking up cut work.

809
01:00:32,590 --> 01:00:36,290
我認為不可能的時候 他總能給我包扎好
He used to patch me up when I thought it was impossible.

810
01:00:37,630 --> 01:00:39,620
有他在賽場邊真不錯
Good man to have in your corner.

811
01:00:40,560 --> 01:00:42,500
是啊
Yes, he is.

812
01:00:44,070 --> 01:00:47,260
我最后一次比賽，在圣伯蒂諾 他也陪了我全場
He stayed with me through my last fight in San Berdu.

813
01:00:48,070 --> 01:00:51,510
我的經理喝醉了，不知所蹤
My manager was off getting drunk somewhere...

814
01:00:52,080 --> 01:00:55,530
只有我和弗蘭基
...and it was just Frankie and me.

815
01:00:57,410 --> 01:01:00,250
我被打得暈頭轉向
I was taking a hellacious beating.

816
01:01:01,690 --> 01:01:05,020
每個人最多能參加多少比賽 都有個數字
Everybody's got a particular number of fights in him.

817
01:01:05,720 --> 01:01:08,660
沒人告訴你那個數字是多少
Nobody tells you what that number is.

818
01:01:09,590 --> 01:01:12,260
我的是109場
Mine was 109.

819
01:01:12,860 --> 01:01:15,130
我只是不愿承認
I just didn't want to admit it.

820
01:01:16,900 --> 01:01:19,230
第四回合
Fourth round, this...

821
01:01:19,940 --> 01:01:21,370
這里被打開了口子
...cut opens up.

822
01:01:21,840 --> 01:01:24,640
鮮血擁進我的眼睛里
Blood starts pouring into my eye.

823
01:01:26,540 --> 01:01:30,500
他們本應該終止那場比賽的 但是，媽的，我是個在圣伯蒂諾的黑人
They should've stopped the fight, but, hell, I was a black man in San Berdu.

824
01:01:30,710 --> 01:01:32,880
我到那里就是去流血的
Blood was what I was there for.

825
01:01:33,750 --> 01:01:37,310
一回合接著一回合 我不斷地讓弗蘭基給我包扎
Round after round, I kept getting Frankie to patch me up.

826
01:01:37,890 --> 01:01:39,880
他想扔毛巾認輸...
He's talking about throwing in the towel...

827
01:01:40,060 --> 01:01:43,390
...但他不是我的經理人 什么也不能扔
...but he ain't my manager, he can't throw in nothing.

828
01:01:44,430 --> 01:01:46,690
一回合接著一回合...
Round after round...

829
01:01:46,860 --> 01:01:49,200
...他一直跟我爭吵
...he's arguing with me.

830
01:01:50,570 --> 01:01:54,660
我幾乎是在笑他，因為，媽的 好象是打在他身上似的
And I'm almost laughing because, hell, it's getting more to him than to me.

831
01:01:55,570 --> 01:01:58,060
我打了15回合
I go 15 rounds...

832
01:01:58,240 --> 01:02:00,470
裁判判我輸了
...Iose by decision.

833
01:02:01,140 --> 01:02:03,510
第二天早上，我的眼睛沒了
Next morning, I lose the eye.

834
01:02:06,020 --> 01:02:09,540
23年來，他從來沒說起過這件事
In 23 years, he's never said a thing about it.

835
01:02:10,490 --> 01:02:14,550
沒這個必要 每次他看我，我都能從他的臉上讀出來
Doesn't have to. I can see it in his face every time he looks at me.

836
01:02:15,390 --> 01:02:17,190
某種程度上
Somehow...

837
01:02:18,160 --> 01:02:20,860
弗蘭基認為自己應該終止那場比賽
...Frankie thinks he should've stopped that fight...

838
01:02:21,700 --> 01:02:24,030
可以挽救我的眼睛
...should've saved my eye.

839
01:02:26,270 --> 01:02:30,370
他一生都希望能收回那第109場比賽
Spends his life wishing he could take back that 109th fight.

840
01:02:31,210 --> 01:02:34,140
但我卻想參加第110場
I wanted to go to 110.

841
01:02:34,740 --> 01:02:36,740
重點是
Thing is...

842
01:02:37,380 --> 01:02:39,210
如果你想取得冠軍
...if you wanna get to the title...

843
01:02:40,520 --> 01:02:43,210
也許他并不是最好人選
...maybe he's not the one to take you there.

844
01:02:48,430 --> 01:02:50,550
你告訴了麥克先生我們今晚會來這里？
You tell Mr.Mack we'd be here tonight?

845
01:02:53,730 --> 01:02:55,960
繼續吃你的蛋糕吧
You go on, eat your cupcake.

846
01:02:56,130 --> 01:02:58,860
不用了，我來吧
No, I got it.

847
01:03:04,410 --> 01:03:05,810
這就是規矩
It's the rule.

848
01:03:05,980 --> 01:03:08,380
隨時保護自己
Always protect yourself.

849
01:03:08,950 --> 01:03:11,780
人們從不采納自己的意見
People never take their own advice.

850
01:03:11,950 --> 01:03:16,980
如果她要離開弗蘭基 最好當時就做
If she was gonna leave Frankie, better she did it to him then.

851
01:03:21,320 --> 01:03:23,290
米奇 麥克先生？
Mr.Mickey Mack?

852
01:03:23,460 --> 01:03:25,790
我是麥琪 菲斯杰拉德
I'm Maggie Fitzgerald.

853
01:03:26,100 --> 01:03:31,830
我聽說你是非常好的經理人 給大個子威利做的很不錯
I hear you're a real good manager, doing good things for Big Willie.

854
01:03:32,270 --> 01:03:35,330
但我想你該知道 我是不會離開鄧先生的
But I thought you should know I ain't never leaving Mr.Dunn...

855
01:03:36,270 --> 01:03:39,260
所以你不需要再找借口好遇見我了
...so you don't need to make any more excuses to bump into me.

856
01:03:41,310 --> 01:03:43,710
不好意思打攪你吃飯了
Sorry for interrupting your dinner.

857
01:03:47,450 --> 01:03:51,610
麥琪總是喜歡剛一交手 就把對手擊倒
Maggie always did like taking them out in the first round.

858
01:04:24,790 --> 01:04:28,660
寄出的信總是原樣退回:
The letters always came back marked the same way:

859
01:04:28,830 --> 01:04:31,020
上面寫著“退還發件人”
"Return to sender."

860
01:05:00,560 --> 01:05:03,080
我給你準備點咖啡
I'll make you some coffee.

861
01:05:05,060 --> 01:05:06,720
你打算拿你的錢干些什么？
What are you doing with your money?

862
01:05:07,330 --> 01:05:09,420
- 存起來    - 好孩子
- Saving it.    - Good girl.

863
01:05:11,270 --> 01:05:14,670
你知道，如果存夠了就可以買座小房
You know, you save enough of it, you ought to get yourself a little house.

864
01:05:14,840 --> 01:05:16,170
現金，不用貸款
Cash, no mortgage.

865
01:05:16,340 --> 01:05:18,900
那還要存一段時間
Gonna be a while before I can do that.

866
01:05:22,010 --> 01:05:25,240
是啊，可能還有一段時間...
Yeah, well, it might be a stretch...

867
01:05:25,420 --> 01:05:28,040
...但你得給自己弄個窩
...but you gotta get yourself a place of your own.

868
01:05:28,220 --> 01:05:31,450
把錢浪費在無關緊要的東西上 你能得到什么？
Go around wasting it on things that don't matter and what do you got?

869
01:05:31,860 --> 01:05:33,320
明白么？
You understand?

870
01:05:33,590 --> 01:05:37,390
很快，如果你等得太久 你什么也得不到
Pretty soon, you wait long enough, you got nothing.

871
01:05:37,560 --> 01:05:39,550
好吧，只要我存夠錢
Okay, soon as I get the money.

872
01:05:39,730 --> 01:05:43,790
我這一生中犯了很多錯誤 我只是不想你走一樣的路
I made a lot of mistakes in my life. I'm just trying to keep you from doing the same.

873
01:05:44,270 --> 01:05:45,890
知道了，老板
I know, boss.

874
01:05:47,200 --> 01:05:49,670
- 我不會長命百歲的    - 這是什么？
- I'm not gonna live forever.    - What is it?

875
01:05:49,840 --> 01:05:52,500
一盒關于你那個英國對手的錄像帶
It's a tape on that girl in England you're gonna fight.

876
01:05:52,780 --> 01:05:56,010
如果你想去爭奪冠軍 我們得做-- 嘿！
If you're gonna go for the title, we got some moves to... Hey.

877
01:05:56,180 --> 01:05:58,840
嘿，快他媽下來 知道我有多大歲數么？
Hey, get the hell down. You know how old I am?

878
01:05:59,020 --> 01:06:01,640
- 謝謝老板，非常感謝    - 嗯
- Thank you, boss. Thank you so much.    - Yeah.

879
01:06:01,820 --> 01:06:06,260
不用謝，親愛的 給，把--我把這個放到機器里去
You're welcome, darling. Here, just... Here, let me put this in the machine.

880
01:06:06,420 --> 01:06:08,450
什么機器？
What machine?

881
01:06:09,060 --> 01:06:10,620
你沒有電視，是么？
Don't have a TV, huh?

882
01:06:10,790 --> 01:06:12,560
沒有
No.

883
01:06:13,230 --> 01:06:14,990
耶！
Yeah!

884
01:06:15,500 --> 01:06:18,190
好了，好的
All right. Okay.

885
01:06:24,270 --> 01:06:26,770
- 還有十分鐘，親愛的    - 謝謝
- Ten minutes, love.    - Thank you.

886
01:06:27,080 --> 01:06:28,510
那家伙說他愛我
Man says he loves me.

887
01:06:28,680 --> 01:06:30,770
他不可能是第一個這么說的男人
He's probably not the first one to say that.

888
01:06:30,950 --> 01:06:33,180
除了我爸以外的第一個
First since my daddy.

889
01:06:33,820 --> 01:06:35,480
我要是贏了，你說他會向我求婚么？
I win, you think he'll propose?

890
01:06:35,850 --> 01:06:37,980
你贏了，我就向你求婚
You win, I'll propose.

891
01:06:41,790 --> 01:06:43,730
看，我給你帶了件禮物
Look, I got you a gift here.

892
01:06:48,930 --> 01:06:50,760
我想這是其他人的吧
I think they gave you somebody else's.

893
01:06:50,930 --> 01:06:52,900
不，不，就是這個
No, no, this is it.

894
01:06:53,940 --> 01:06:55,400
“莫 庫什勒”是什么意思？
What's it mean?

895
01:06:55,570 --> 01:06:59,410
不知道，是高盧語
I don't know. Just something in Gaelic.

896
01:07:00,340 --> 01:07:04,040
- 真漂亮    - 嗯，我也這么認為
- It's beautiful.    - Yeah, I thought so.

897
01:07:04,210 --> 01:07:06,040
- 是啊    - 真絲的
- Yeah.    - Real silk thread.

898
01:07:09,650 --> 01:07:13,990
來自美國的挑戰者...
From the United States of America, the challenger...

899
01:07:14,160 --> 01:07:17,490
...麥琪 菲斯杰拉德
...Maggie Fitzgerald.

900
01:07:19,260 --> 01:07:21,360
“莫 庫什勒” 你看到她袍子上的字了嗎？
Mo cuishle. Did you see what was on her robe?

901
01:07:21,530 --> 01:07:23,800
- “莫 庫什勒”，“莫 庫什勒”    - “莫 庫什勒”
- Mo cuishle. Mo cuishle.    - Mo cuishle.

902
01:07:28,000 --> 01:07:29,870
她本不是本晚的賣點
She wasn 't the main attraction.

903
01:07:30,040 --> 01:07:33,700
她的比賽是一場中量級拳王賽的墊場賽
She was on the undercard of a middleweight title fight.

904
01:07:34,080 --> 01:07:36,070
但如果你問問在場的人...
But ask someone who was there...

905
01:07:36,250 --> 01:07:39,240
...他們都不記得 當晚參加比賽的其他選手了
...they couldn 't tell you who else fought that night.

906
01:07:45,390 --> 01:07:47,050
開始
Box.

907
01:08:07,610 --> 01:08:09,100
- 加油！    -“莫 庫什勒”！
- Come on!    - Mo cuishle!

908
01:08:09,810 --> 01:08:13,980
“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！
Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle!

909
01:08:15,180 --> 01:08:16,810
“莫 庫什勒”！
Mo cuishle!

910
01:08:18,120 --> 01:08:19,210
“莫 庫什勒”！
Mo cuishle!

911
01:08:21,090 --> 01:08:24,080
“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！
Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle!

912
01:08:32,870 --> 01:08:34,600
她很強
She's tough.

913
01:08:36,310 --> 01:08:38,740
我無法靠近 我無法靠近打到她
I can't get inside. I can't get close enough to hit her.

914
01:08:38,910 --> 01:08:41,380
- 你知道為什么嗎？    - 為什么？
- You know why that is?    - Why?

915
01:08:41,810 --> 01:08:43,750
因為她是個比你更好的拳手
She's a better fighter than you are.

916
01:08:43,910 --> 01:08:48,010
她更年輕，更強壯 更有經驗
She's younger, she's stronger, and she's more experienced. Now...

917
01:08:48,180 --> 01:08:50,380
現在你打算怎么辦？
...what are you gonna do about it?

918
01:08:58,430 --> 01:09:00,190
去吧
Get in there.

919
01:09:00,930 --> 01:09:02,490
開始
Box.

920
01:09:16,150 --> 01:09:20,910
三，四，五，六..
Three, four, five, six...

921
01:09:21,080 --> 01:09:26,250
...七，八，九，十
...seven, eight, nine, ten.

922
01:09:26,960 --> 01:09:30,520
“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！
Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle!

923
01:09:37,670 --> 01:09:41,000
- “莫 庫什勒”！    - “莫 庫什勒”！
- Mo cuishle!    - Mo cuishle!

924
01:09:48,180 --> 01:09:50,340
你知道我可以問其他人，對嗎？
I could ask someone, you know?

925
01:09:50,910 --> 01:09:52,240
好啊
Good.

926
01:09:52,420 --> 01:09:54,440
你知道以后告訴我
You find out, you let me know.

927
01:10:01,690 --> 01:10:04,460
不管那個名字是什么意思 人們記住了
Whatever it meant, the name stuck.

928
01:10:04,630 --> 01:10:09,190
麥琪打遍愛丁堡，巴黎，布魯塞爾 和阿姆斯特丹
Maggie fought in Edinburgh and Paris, Brussels and Amsterdam.

929
01:10:09,370 --> 01:10:12,200
觀眾總是高呼“莫 庫什勒”
It was always mo cuishle.

930
01:10:12,440 --> 01:10:14,770
看起來到處是愛爾蘭人...
Seems there are Irish people everywhere...

931
01:10:14,940 --> 01:10:17,270
...或者是想成為愛爾蘭人的人
...or people who wanna be.

932
01:10:17,670 --> 01:10:20,160
當他們回到美國的時候...
By the time they came back to the States...

933
01:10:21,010 --> 01:10:24,100
...麥琪已經達到了一個新的水平
...Maggie was in a whole new league.

934
01:10:41,230 --> 01:10:45,690
“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！“莫 庫什勒”！
Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle! Mo cuishle!

935
01:10:55,550 --> 01:10:58,710
后來他們受到另一場冠軍賽的邀請
After that they got another offer to fight for the title.

936
01:11:01,080 --> 01:11:02,950
怎么分成？
What's the split?

937
01:11:03,520 --> 01:11:05,950
- 六四開    - 好
- Sixty-forty.    - Good.

938
01:11:06,120 --> 01:11:10,080
好，我們六，你們四 因為麥琪是吸引觀眾的籌碼
We'll take 60 and you take 40, being as that Maggie's the draw.

939
01:11:10,590 --> 01:11:11,990
那個小女孩
That little girl?

940
01:11:12,400 --> 01:11:15,730
你真的認為我說的不對？ 你認為觀眾會說...
You think I'm wrong, really? You think people are saying...

941
01:11:15,900 --> 01:11:19,700
...他們想看一個破爛德國人 痛揍無名氏小姐？
...that they wanna see some scabby Kraut beat up on little Miss What's-Her-Name?

942
01:11:19,870 --> 01:11:22,930
你要能找到那樣的人，我們就拿四
You find someone who says that, and we'll take the 40.

943
01:11:30,480 --> 01:11:32,170
給你
There you go.

944
01:11:35,080 --> 01:11:38,880
他們現在是六四開 不過最后會是五五開
They're at 60-40, but they'll come up to 50-50.

945
01:11:39,660 --> 01:11:41,380
那女孩現在怎么樣了？
How's that girl doing?

946
01:11:41,560 --> 01:11:44,690
她腦震蕩了，耳鼓膜破裂
Well, she's got a concussion and a broken eardrum.

947
01:11:44,860 --> 01:11:46,800
她沒事吧
She be all right?

948
01:11:47,060 --> 01:11:50,860
- 她要是有事呢？    - 也許我應該給她送點什么
- And if she isn't?    - Maybe I should send her something.

949
01:11:51,030 --> 01:11:55,200
你愿意的話，把你的獎金寄給她好了 我想她會接受
Well, you could send her your check if you'd like. I'm sure she'd take it.

950
01:12:00,210 --> 01:12:01,970
老板？
Boss?

951
01:12:02,140 --> 01:12:04,010
我們說起過的那座房子？
That little house we talked about?

952
01:12:04,650 --> 01:12:05,840
我買下了
I bought it.

953
01:12:06,550 --> 01:12:08,880
聰明的姑娘
Well, smart girl.

954
01:12:09,550 --> 01:12:13,350
給我媽買的 離她現在住的地方不到一英里
For my mama. It's only about a mile from where she lives now.

955
01:12:13,520 --> 01:12:15,650
如你所言，沒有貸款
No mortgage, just like you said.

956
01:12:17,890 --> 01:12:19,990
你是個好女兒
You're a good daughter.

957
01:12:20,630 --> 01:12:22,720
她還不知道
She don't know about it yet.

958
01:12:22,900 --> 01:12:26,430
我希望我們可以多待一天 開車到那里去
I was hoping maybe we could stay an extra day, drive over there?

959
01:12:26,600 --> 01:12:28,540
我知道她想見你
I know she wants to meet you.

960
01:12:31,210 --> 01:12:33,730
好吧，可以
Yeah, we could do that.

961
01:12:50,790 --> 01:12:53,960
哦，天哪，媽媽快出來
Oh, my God. Mama, come on out here.

962
01:12:54,130 --> 01:12:56,330
麥琪回來了
Mary M's here.

963
01:13:13,380 --> 01:13:17,440
- 這是約翰遜家的舊屋    - 不再是了
- This is the Johnsons' old house.    - Not anymore.

964
01:13:21,160 --> 01:13:24,990
它是你的了，媽媽 還有瑪代爾和孩子們
It's all yours, Mama. For you and Mardell and the kids.

965
01:13:25,160 --> 01:13:28,960
- 麥琪，這房子是你給我買的？    - 對，是你的了，全部付清了
- Mary M, you bought this for me?    - Yeah, all yours, free and clear.

966
01:13:29,130 --> 01:13:30,830
親愛的
Darling...

967
01:13:31,070 --> 01:13:33,330
沒冰箱，也沒爐灶
There's no fridge. No stove neither.

968
01:13:33,500 --> 01:13:35,800
在你們搬進來前，會準備好的
They'll be here before you move in.

969
01:13:37,040 --> 01:13:39,440
- 你花了多少錢？    - 你不用管
- How much money did this cost you?    - Never mind that.

970
01:13:39,610 --> 01:13:42,300
- 你不該這么做    - 您需要一個體面的住處
- You shouldn't have done this.    - You need a decent place.

971
01:13:42,480 --> 01:13:45,780
你不該這么做 你該先問問我的
You shouldn't have done it. You should've asked me first.

972
01:13:47,150 --> 01:13:50,380
如果政府發現了 他們會停掉我的社會福利的
Government's gonna find out about this, they're gonna stop my welfare.

973
01:13:50,550 --> 01:13:54,390
- 媽媽，他們不會的    - 他們會的，你很好，有自己的工作
- Mama, no, they ain't.    - They are. You're fine, you're working...

974
01:13:54,560 --> 01:13:56,420
但沒有福利我活不下去
...but I can't live without my welfare.

975
01:13:56,590 --> 01:13:58,250
媽媽我會給你寄錢的
Mama, I'll send you money.

976
01:13:58,530 --> 01:14:01,830
醫療怎么辦？ 公費醫療會把我從名單上劃掉
What about my medicine? Medicaid gonna cut me off.

977
01:14:02,000 --> 01:14:05,630
- 我拿什么錢買藥啊？    - 我會給你寄更多的錢
- How am I supposed to get my medicine?    - I'll send you more money.

978
01:14:05,970 --> 01:14:08,230
我希望你沒有預期JD要住進來
I hope you don't expect J.D. To move in with us.

979
01:14:08,400 --> 01:14:09,670
你知道他快出獄了
He's getting out, you know.

980
01:14:10,440 --> 01:14:12,870
為什么不把錢直接給我？
Why didn't you just give me the money?

981
01:14:13,880 --> 01:14:16,500
為什么必須給我買房子？
Why'd you have to buy me a house?

982
01:14:17,650 --> 01:14:22,240
不是必須，媽媽，但房子是你的了
I didn't have to, Mama, but it's yours.

983
01:14:22,420 --> 01:14:24,580
如果想要錢，把它賣掉好了
You want the money, sell it.

984
01:14:31,130 --> 01:14:32,750
我不--
I don't...

985
01:14:39,300 --> 01:14:41,200
我知道你不想傷害我們...
I know you didn't mean nothing hurtful...

986
01:14:41,370 --> 01:14:43,770
...只是有時候你沒把事情想清楚
...but sometimes you just don't think things through.

987
01:14:43,940 --> 01:14:47,470
- 這倒是真的，媽媽    - 我會試著不把房子賣掉
- That's true, Mama.    - I'll try and keep the house.

988
01:14:47,980 --> 01:14:50,310
我只是擔心養房子的那些費用
I'm just worried about all those expenses.

989
01:14:50,480 --> 01:14:52,380
我會給你寄更多錢的
I'll send you some more money.

990
01:15:01,560 --> 01:15:03,790
那個人把你打成這樣的？
That man hitting you?

991
01:15:05,330 --> 01:15:07,490
這是比賽留下的
It's from the fight.

992
01:15:07,860 --> 01:15:09,420
我是一名拳擊手，媽媽
I'm a fighter, Mama.

993
01:15:10,300 --> 01:15:12,270
找個老公吧，麥琪
Find a man, Mary M.

994
01:15:12,440 --> 01:15:14,100
過正常的生活
Live proper.

995
01:15:14,270 --> 01:15:17,260
人們知道你的職業后就會嘲笑你
People hear about what you're doing and they laugh.

996
01:15:17,440 --> 01:15:20,500
告訴你我很難過，但是他們嘲笑你
Hurts me to tell you, but they laugh at you.

997
01:16:12,190 --> 01:16:13,990
嗨
Hi.

998
01:16:44,090 --> 01:16:46,420
你養過狗么？
You ever own a dog?

999
01:16:46,590 --> 01:16:48,120
沒有
Nope.

1000
01:16:48,290 --> 01:16:52,890
我差點養了一只巴斯頓的中型狗
Closest I ever came was a middleweight from Barstow.

1001
01:16:54,930 --> 01:16:59,300
我爸養過一只德國牧羊犬，埃克斯
My daddy had a German shepherd, Axel.

1002
01:16:59,470 --> 01:17:01,170
埃克斯的后腿不太好
Axel's hindquarters were so bad...

1003
01:17:01,340 --> 01:17:04,940
它得用自己的前腿拖著自己 從一個房間走到另一個房間
...he had to drag himself room to room by his front legs.

1004
01:17:05,110 --> 01:17:08,080
看他跑過廚房的地板
Me and Mardell would bust up laughing...

1005
01:17:08,250 --> 01:17:12,080
我和瑪代爾都會忍不住大笑
...watching him scoot across the kitchen floor.

1006
01:17:12,580 --> 01:17:16,350
爸爸，他當時病的很重 自己都站不起來
Daddy, he was so sick by then, he couldn't hardly stand himself.

1007
01:17:17,720 --> 01:17:21,280
但一天早上他起床以后 把埃克斯抱到他的拖車上
But one morning he got up, carried Axel to his rig...

1008
01:17:21,460 --> 01:17:25,860
他們倆跑進樹林里 又唱又叫
...and the two of them went off into the woods, singing and howling.

1009
01:17:26,630 --> 01:17:30,090
直到那天晚上他獨自回來時
But it wasn't till he got home that night alone that I saw...

1010
01:17:30,270 --> 01:17:32,900
我才發現卡車里的鏟子
...the shovel in the back of the truck.

1011
01:17:37,880 --> 01:17:40,640
好想再看看他們倆在一起的樣子
Sure miss watching the two of them together.

1012
01:17:49,620 --> 01:17:52,110
我現在除了你誰都沒有了，弗蘭基
I got nobody but you, Frankie.

1013
01:17:55,390 --> 01:17:57,260
對，你還有我
Well, you've got me.

1014
01:17:59,730 --> 01:18:03,900
至少在你找到一個好經理人以前是這樣
At least, that is, until we find you a good manager.

1015
01:18:11,880 --> 01:18:15,810
嘿，我們能在這停一下么？
Hey, can we stop just up here?

1016
01:18:16,150 --> 01:18:17,880
好
Yeah.

1017
01:18:18,420 --> 01:18:21,350
這里有附近最好的檸檬派
This place has the best lemon pie around.

1018
01:18:21,520 --> 01:18:24,460
沒有那種惡心的罐裝餡
None of that canned-filling crap.

1019
01:18:39,040 --> 01:18:41,700
現在我可以上天堂了
Now I can die and go to heaven.

1020
01:18:46,580 --> 01:18:48,550
我以前和爸爸常來這
I used to come here with Daddy.

1021
01:18:49,720 --> 01:18:52,240
我不知道象這樣的地方會不會出售
Wonder if a place like this is for sale.

1022
01:18:52,420 --> 01:18:54,940
我還有點積蓄
I got a little bit of savings.

1023
01:18:59,700 --> 01:19:01,530
（艾記小吃店）

1024
01:19:01,990 --> 01:19:04,520
好，好，謝謝
That's fine, fine, thanks.

1025
01:19:09,230 --> 01:19:11,330
嘿，丹吉爾到底在看什么？
Hey, what the hell's Danger looking at?

1026
01:19:12,140 --> 01:19:14,400
好像是另外一瓶水
Looks like another bottle of water.

1027
01:19:14,570 --> 01:19:16,910
想和我們一起到拉斯維加斯去么？
Wanna come to Vegas with us?

1028
01:19:17,280 --> 01:19:22,040
看你們在老虎機那兒受罪？ 我的心臟受不了那種刺激
Watch you suffer over the nickel slots? My heart can't take that kind of pounding.

1029
01:19:22,210 --> 01:19:25,810
呃，她有場冠軍賽，對手是“蘭熊”
Well, she's got a title shot. The Blue Bear.

1030
01:19:25,980 --> 01:19:28,010
百萬美金對半分
Million dollars, split right down the center.

1031
01:19:28,190 --> 01:19:29,980
啊，不錯啊，弗蘭基，很不錯
That's good, Frankie. That's real good.

1032
01:19:30,160 --> 01:19:31,750
我想找個好助手一起去
Well, I could use a good second.

1033
01:19:31,920 --> 01:19:33,690
但是找不到 所以我來問問你
Can't find one, I thought I'd ask you.

1034
01:19:33,860 --> 01:19:35,950
哦，我他媽為什么會同意呢？
Now, why the hell would I wanna do that?

1035
01:19:36,500 --> 01:19:40,560
因為你是一個 從來沒得過冠軍的半瞎的老傻瓜
Well, because you're a half-blind old fool who never got there himself.

1036
01:19:40,730 --> 01:19:44,460
我想你可能想去體驗一下 站在冠軍賽的繩圈里的感覺
I thought you might like to feel what it's like to be in a ring on a title match.

1037
01:19:44,640 --> 01:19:46,630
不好意思，我替你遺憾了
Excuse me for feeling sorry for you.

1038
01:19:47,810 --> 01:19:50,270
我不去，你還是在拉斯維加斯找吧
No, you pick up somebody there in Vegas.

1039
01:19:51,810 --> 01:19:53,510
找個年輕點的
Somebody with young hands.

1040
01:19:53,680 --> 01:19:56,740
你不會哭吧？ 我已經帶上一個女孩了
You're not gonna cry now, are you? I've already got one girl.

1041
01:19:58,550 --> 01:20:00,420
如果我離開這地方一天...
I leave this place for one day...

1042
01:20:00,590 --> 01:20:03,420
...知道回來時這里會變成什么樣么？
...got any idea what it would look like when I come back?

1043
01:20:03,590 --> 01:20:05,420
和現在這樣差不多吧
Kind of like it looks right now.

1044
01:20:05,590 --> 01:20:07,020
噢，去死吧
Oh, go to hell.

1045
01:20:08,830 --> 01:20:11,920
告訴麥琪沒有拳王腰帶不要回來
You tell Maggie don't come back here without a belt.

1046
01:20:12,330 --> 01:20:13,890
知道了
Will do.

1047
01:20:17,970 --> 01:20:19,940
嘿，斯科雷普先生
Hey, Mr.Scrap.

1048
01:20:20,110 --> 01:20:23,400
我有個問題 可是我覺得問出來好傻
I got a question, but I feel real stupid asking it.

1049
01:20:23,580 --> 01:20:25,810
在這里沒有問題是愚蠢的，丹吉爾
No such thing as a stupid question there, Danger.

1050
01:20:25,980 --> 01:20:27,780
好吧
Okay.

1051
01:20:30,050 --> 01:20:34,110
你怎么把冰塊從這么小的口里放進去的？
How'd you get all the ice in here through this little tiny hole?

1052
01:20:34,290 --> 01:20:36,350
我一直在想
I've been thinking on it.

1053
01:20:36,520 --> 01:20:38,280
但想不出來
Can't figure it out.

1054
01:20:38,460 --> 01:20:40,080
我來做給你看吧，丹吉爾
Why don't I show you, Danger.

1055
01:20:40,260 --> 01:20:43,630
- 你可以，你可以做給我看？    - 我想可以，我想可以
- You could do that? You could show me?    - I think so. I think so.

1056
01:20:43,800 --> 01:20:48,820
還有，斯科雷普先生 我有點覺得我準備好參加比賽了
Also, Mr.Scrap, I was kind of thinking I might be ready for a fight.

1057
01:20:52,640 --> 01:20:55,130
我拿了票，你準備好了么？
Well, I got the tickets. You ready?

1058
01:20:55,310 --> 01:20:58,210
- 我們坐飛機去？    - 你寧愿開車？
- We're flying?    - Would you rather drive?

1059
01:20:59,580 --> 01:21:01,310
你是問我嗎？
You're asking me?

1060
01:21:01,910 --> 01:21:04,710
你是想坐飛機還是開車過去？
Would you rather fly, or would you rather drive?

1061
01:21:05,350 --> 01:21:07,650
我終于有權決定某些事了么？
So I finally get to decide something?

1062
01:21:07,820 --> 01:21:09,220
我說的就是這個意思
That's what I'm saying.

1063
01:21:09,760 --> 01:21:10,980
好吧
Fine.

1064
01:21:11,160 --> 01:21:12,890
好，飛過去，開車回來
Fly there, drive back.

1065
01:21:13,360 --> 01:21:16,920
這是我聽過的最愚蠢的事 我們怎么會那么做？
That's the stupidest thing I've ever heard. How the hell we gonna do that?

1066
01:21:17,230 --> 01:21:18,860
你說過讓我決定的
You said it was up to me.

1067
01:21:29,010 --> 01:21:31,270
丹吉爾，給他們點顏色
Give them hell there, Danger.

1068
01:21:31,440 --> 01:21:34,470
嘿，老家伙，馬桶的水溢出來了
Hey, old school, the toilet's overflowing.

1069
01:21:38,820 --> 01:21:41,620
嘿，冒失鬼，過來一下
Hey, Flippy, come here for a minute.

1070
01:21:43,620 --> 01:21:45,350
我的天啊
Jesus.

1071
01:21:45,660 --> 01:21:48,220
老天爺
Jesus, Mary and Joseph.

1072
01:21:48,690 --> 01:21:50,820
噢，上帝！
Oh, God!

1073
01:21:55,230 --> 01:21:56,530
蠢豬
Dumb-ass.

1074
01:21:56,940 --> 01:21:59,370
來呀，丹吉爾 來呀，丹吉爾
Come on, Danger. Come on, Danger.

1075
01:21:59,540 --> 01:22:00,940
來呀，防守
Come on. Defense!

1076
01:22:01,610 --> 01:22:03,870
本來我可以坐在海市蜃樓酒店里...
Could be sitting up at the Mirage...

1077
01:22:04,640 --> 01:22:06,580
...喝著邁泰酒...
...drinking mai tais...

1078
01:22:07,450 --> 01:22:08,940
...看著裸體女人
...Iooking at naked women.

