01:39:51,710 --> 01:39:54,010
一，二，三，起
One, two, three, up.

1244
01:39:56,410 --> 01:39:58,750
由于她無法自主呼吸
Since she couldn't breathe on her own...

1245
01:39:58,920 --> 01:40:01,540
呼吸器總是開著
...her respirators were always on.

1246
01:40:02,790 --> 01:40:06,620
氧氣24小時不間斷地 被輸進她的身體里
Oxygen was pumped into her 24 hours a day.

1247
01:40:32,780 --> 01:40:36,180
麥琪的媽媽打電話來說 他們會來看她
Maggie's mama called to say they were all coming for a visit.

1248
01:40:36,350 --> 01:40:39,980
在接下來的兩周里 她每天都在窗前等他們
She waited by the window every day for the next two weeks.

1249
01:40:40,960 --> 01:40:42,260
當然
Sure.

1250
01:40:42,430 --> 01:40:45,020
弗蘭基最后終于追蹤到了他們
Frankie finally tracked them down.

1251
01:40:45,200 --> 01:40:49,190
發現他們六天前就住進旅館了
Learned they'd checked into their hotel six days earlier.

1252
01:40:49,370 --> 01:40:52,730
弗蘭基一直給他們留言 但總沒有回音
Kept leaving messages which were never returned.

1253
01:40:56,810 --> 01:40:59,500
你不用整天都待在這兒
You don't have to hang around all day.

1254
01:41:03,310 --> 01:41:06,310
我喜歡這里，沒關系的
I like it here. I don't mind.

1255
01:41:07,050 --> 01:41:11,010
其實就算你不在，我也會來讀書的
In fact, if you weren't here, I'd come here anyway to read my books.

1256
01:41:13,890 --> 01:41:16,860
媽媽馬上會來分擔一些負擔的
Mama will be here soon to share some of the burden.

1257
01:41:17,230 --> 01:41:19,030
哦，這不是什么負擔
Well, it's no burden.

1258
01:41:19,960 --> 01:41:21,400
給
Here.

1259
01:41:23,430 --> 01:41:24,730
讀讀這個
Read this.

1260
01:41:33,880 --> 01:41:35,970
好了，好了，行了
Okay, okay, that's enough.

1261
01:41:36,450 --> 01:41:37,910
讀得太糟糕了
That's terrible.

1262
01:41:40,380 --> 01:41:43,410
我給你翻成英文吧
Anyway, I'll tell you in English what you were saying.

1263
01:41:46,320 --> 01:41:47,790
上面說：
It says:

1264
01:41:47,960 --> 01:41:51,520
“我要起身去了，去往那茵湖島”
I will arise and go now And go to Innisfree

1265
01:41:51,700 --> 01:41:56,220
“用泥土和樹枝，蓋上一間小木房”
And a small cabin build there Of clay and wattles made

1266
01:41:57,130 --> 01:42:01,540
“我享受著彼方的寧靜，它緩緩滴零”
And I shall have some peace there For peace comes dropping slow

1267
01:42:02,140 --> 01:42:06,840
“從晨曦的面紗，到蟋蟀歌唱的地方”
Dropping from the veils of the morning To where the cricket sings.

1268
01:42:09,210 --> 01:42:10,610
還不賴，對吧？
Not bad, huh?

1269
01:42:15,090 --> 01:42:17,280
你要蓋一間小木屋么，老板？
You gonna build a cabin, boss?

1270
01:42:17,960 --> 01:42:19,790
- 我？    - 對
- Me?    - Yeah.

1271
01:42:22,160 --> 01:42:24,890
你知道，等你收山之后
You know, when you quit all this.

1272
01:42:26,860 --> 01:42:28,490
你是說拳擊？
You mean boxing?

1273
01:42:29,070 --> 01:42:31,690
不，我永遠不會收山的
No, I'll never quit.

1274
01:42:32,700 --> 01:42:35,190
我太喜歡那汗臭味道了，我想
I like the stink too much, I guess.

1275
01:42:41,080 --> 01:42:43,600
你想？我看你邊看書...
You think? Because I could see you there real easy...

1276
01:42:43,780 --> 01:42:46,150
...邊吃檸檬派很愜意呀
...with your books and lemon pie.

1277
01:42:48,320 --> 01:42:51,220
你呢？想在小木屋里生活么？
How about you? Would you like to go live in a cabin?

1278
01:42:53,260 --> 01:42:55,520
我可以學怎么烤東西
I could learn how to bake.

1279
01:42:59,460 --> 01:43:00,990
那樣的話，我....
Well, then, I'II...

1280
01:43:01,170 --> 01:43:03,330
我也許要開始找了
Maybe I'll start looking then.

1281
01:43:25,060 --> 01:43:26,550
是啊
Yeah.

1282
01:43:29,330 --> 01:43:31,730
- 去吧    - 好的，聽起來不錯
- Go ahead.    - All right. Okay, sounds good.

1283
01:43:35,630 --> 01:43:38,030
嘿，我是弗蘭基 鄧 我們在密蘇里見過
Hi, I'm Frankie Dunn. I met you back out in Missouri.

1284
01:43:38,200 --> 01:43:39,500
我女兒在哪？
Where's my little girl?

1285
01:43:39,670 --> 01:43:42,500
你們不應該回旅館換身衣服再來嗎？
Don't you think you ought to go back to the hotel and change?

1286
01:43:42,670 --> 01:43:45,440
她還不知道你們已經來了一周 忙著拜訪米老鼠呢
She doesn't know you've been here a week visiting Woody and Mickey.

1287
01:43:45,610 --> 01:43:49,070
我們和我妹妹有正事談 你干嗎不干脆告訴我們她在哪呢？
We got business with my sister. Why don't you just tell us where she is.

1288
01:43:49,250 --> 01:43:52,010
你肯定是JD 那你肯定是那個談正經事的家伙？
Oh, you must be J.D. And you must be the business guy?

1289
01:43:52,180 --> 01:43:53,580
你們錯過了一些東西
There's some rides you missed.

1290
01:43:53,750 --> 01:43:56,410
你們不如回去 我來告訴她你們來不成了
Why don't you go back. I'll tell her you couldn't make it.

1291
01:43:56,590 --> 01:43:58,850
我開了這么遠的路來照顧孩子
I drove all the way here to take care of my child.

1292
01:43:59,020 --> 01:44:01,180
你卻暗示我不是個好母親？
And you're suggesting I'm not a good mother?

1293
01:44:01,360 --> 01:44:03,020
麥琪哪里都去不了
Mary M. Can't go nowhere.

1294
01:44:03,190 --> 01:44:06,160
否則我們早帶她去逛迪斯尼樂園了
If we could've taken her to Disneyland, we would've.

1295
01:44:07,700 --> 01:44:08,890
麥琪 菲斯杰拉德?
Margaret Fitzgerald?

1296
01:44:09,370 --> 01:44:11,060
就在這里，301房間
Right down here, 301.

1297
01:44:11,370 --> 01:44:13,060
- 快來，媽媽    - 我們走
- Come on, Mama.    - Let's go.

1298
01:44:19,580 --> 01:44:21,670
后來我看到自己呼吸
And I saw myself breathing.

1299
01:44:21,850 --> 01:44:23,710
我的身體上下起伏
Like, my body was going up and down.

1300
01:44:23,880 --> 01:44:26,710
我想，“為什么沒人告訴我？”
I thought, "Why didn't somebody tell me?"

1301
01:44:30,190 --> 01:44:33,050
你的頭發得洗了 有點太油了
Your hair needs washing. It's kind of greasy.

1302
01:44:47,140 --> 01:44:48,500
只是些....
It's just a...

1303
01:44:49,510 --> 01:44:51,600
只是些法律上的程序
It's just some kind of legal thing.

1304
01:44:51,810 --> 01:44:53,110
是什么？
What is it?

1305
01:44:53,280 --> 01:44:55,340
你們談得怎樣了？
How we all doing here?

1306
01:44:55,510 --> 01:44:58,040
不好意思，親愛的 我們時間不多
Sorry, darling, but we ain't got a lot of time.

1307
01:44:58,220 --> 01:45:02,380
約翰遜先生收了我們一大筆錢 來保證這件事不出紕漏
Mr.Johnson's charging us a lot of money to be here to make sure this is done proper.

1308
01:45:02,550 --> 01:45:05,180
你們不如把那個留下 我等會兒讀給她聽
Why don't you just leave that. I'll read it to her later.

1309
01:45:05,360 --> 01:45:06,910
嘿，老家伙
Hey, old man...

1310
01:45:07,090 --> 01:45:08,560
你是我們家人么？
...you part of our family?

1311
01:45:09,490 --> 01:45:11,150
別管閑事
Stay the hell out of this.

1312
01:45:12,760 --> 01:45:14,490
念給我聽，媽媽
Read it to me, Mama.

1313
01:45:14,670 --> 01:45:18,230
只是些法律程序 用來保護你的錢的
Well, it's just something legal to protect your money.

1314
01:45:19,000 --> 01:45:20,530
媽媽你不用擔心
Mama, you don't have to worry.

1315
01:45:21,370 --> 01:45:24,810
拳擊協會會支付這里所有的費用的
The boxing commission's paying for all this, everything.

1316
01:45:25,180 --> 01:45:27,300
如果不呢，麥琪？
But what if they don't, Mary M?

1317
01:45:27,480 --> 01:45:30,310
約翰遜先生說他們可以收走我的房子
Mr.Johnson says they can take my house.

1318
01:45:30,480 --> 01:45:33,640
如果你把財產轉移給你母親 那就沒人能動得了了
If you assign your assets to your mother, no one can touch them.

1319
01:45:33,820 --> 01:45:35,650
不用管醫生，喪葬費什么的
No doctors, no funeral expenses.

1320
01:45:36,450 --> 01:45:39,450
- 什么都不用理會了    - 你看，不如你們把這個留下
- Nothing.    - Yeah, look, why don't you just leave it.

1321
01:45:39,620 --> 01:45:43,490
- 我以后再讀給她--    - 無意冒犯，這不關你的事
- Then I'll just read it to her later on...    - With respect, this ain't your business.

1322
01:45:45,000 --> 01:45:47,400
好吧，我在走廊里等
All right. I'll be out in the hall.

1323
01:45:53,640 --> 01:45:56,000
你一直是個好女兒，麥琪
You been a good daughter, Mary M.

1324
01:45:57,610 --> 01:45:59,370
你簽了這份文件
You sign that paper...

1325
01:45:59,780 --> 01:46:01,870
就能照顧你一家
...it'll take care of your family...

1326
01:46:02,180 --> 01:46:04,410
正如你父親所愿
...the way your daddy would've wanted you to.

1327
01:46:09,190 --> 01:46:11,180
嗯，你怎么簽字呢？
How do you make your mark?

1328
01:46:13,720 --> 01:46:14,920
能拿住筆么？
Can you hold a pen?

1329
01:46:15,090 --> 01:46:17,460
她只能用牙齒，媽媽
She gotta do it with her teeth, Mama.

1330
01:46:17,630 --> 01:46:19,690
你得把筆放到她嘴里去
You gotta put it in her mouth.

1331
01:46:21,100 --> 01:46:22,790
好了，親愛的
Here you go, honey.

1332
01:46:25,940 --> 01:46:28,000
你看了那場比賽么，媽媽？
Did you see the fight, Mama?

1333
01:46:28,270 --> 01:46:30,430
親愛的 你知道我對那東西是什么感覺
Honey, you know how I feel about that.

1334
01:46:31,940 --> 01:46:33,570
我打得不錯
I did pretty good.

1335
01:46:33,740 --> 01:46:35,610
你輸了，麥琪
You lost, Mary M.

1336
01:46:36,550 --> 01:46:40,240
聽說不是你的錯，但你輸了
Ain't your fault, the way I heard it, but you lost.

1337
01:46:41,890 --> 01:46:44,620
不能把你現在剩下的東西也輸掉
Don't wanna lose the rest of what you got left.

1338
01:46:45,060 --> 01:46:46,610
對了
There you go.

1339
01:46:55,930 --> 01:46:57,830
你怎么了？
What happened to you?

1340
01:46:58,170 --> 01:46:59,860
這是什么意思？
Well, what's that supposed to mean?

1341
01:47:01,710 --> 01:47:05,140
媽媽，你帶上瑪代爾和JD回家吧
Mama, you take Mardell and J.D. And get home.

1342
01:47:06,980 --> 01:47:10,310
別等我告訴律師 你擔心領不到社會福利...
Before I tell that lawyer that you were so worried about your welfare...

1343
01:47:10,480 --> 01:47:13,710
...所以根本就沒按規定 簽那些房產的證明
...you never signed those house papers like you were supposed to.

1344
01:47:16,550 --> 01:47:18,950
所以只要我愿意 我可以把房子賣了...
So any time I feel like it, I can sell that house...

1345
01:47:19,120 --> 01:47:22,350
...不用理你這個又肥又懶的鄉巴佬
...from under your fat, lazy, hillbilly asses.

1346
01:47:24,460 --> 01:47:27,730
如果你敢再來，我就那么做
And if you ever come back, that's exactly what I'll do.

1347
01:48:09,040 --> 01:48:13,170
也許應該有人數點到10
Well, maybe someone ought to count to 10.

1348
01:48:26,720 --> 01:48:28,850
不是很好聞吧，醫生？
Don't smell real pretty, does it, doc?

1349
01:48:31,800 --> 01:48:33,390
可能保不住了，麥琪
We might have to lose it, Maggie.

1350
01:49:50,370 --> 01:49:53,240
他們拿掉了我的腿，老板
They took my leg, boss.

1351
01:49:58,120 --> 01:50:00,580
不會有事的，聽到嗎？
It's gonna be all right, you hear?

1352
01:50:01,420 --> 01:50:04,820
我總能聽到你的聲音，老板
I always hear your voice, boss.

1353
01:50:36,590 --> 01:50:38,110
需要什么嗎？
You need anything?

1354
01:50:41,930 --> 01:50:44,520
我想知道“莫 庫什勒”的意思
I need to know what "mo cuishle" means.

1355
01:50:46,260 --> 01:50:48,060
可是你沒有贏啊
But you didn't win.

1356
01:50:48,670 --> 01:50:50,570
我不用告訴你的
I don't have to tell you.

1357
01:50:54,300 --> 01:50:56,860
你是我見過的最壞的人
You're the meanest man I ever met.

1358
01:50:57,040 --> 01:50:59,340
難怪沒有人愛你
No wonder no one loves you.

1359
01:51:02,910 --> 01:51:05,310
你讓我想起了我父親
You remind me of my daddy.

1360
01:51:08,020 --> 01:51:09,990
他肯定是個...
Well, he must have been...

1361
01:51:10,490 --> 01:51:13,790
...非常聰明，英俊的人
...a very intelligent, handsome man.

1362
01:51:17,630 --> 01:51:20,790
你不會再讓我讀葉芝了，對吧？
You ain't gonna make me talk no more Yeats, are you?

1363
01:51:22,700 --> 01:51:24,130
不，我...
No, I was...

1364
01:51:25,640 --> 01:51:28,540
...正在看城市大學的宣傳材料
...Iooking at this catalog from City College.

1365
01:51:30,840 --> 01:51:33,170
我想給你弄個輪椅...
I thought I'd get you a wheelchair...

1366
01:51:33,610 --> 01:51:37,050
...可以用吸管控制的那種
...maybe the kind that operates by blowing through a straw.

1367
01:51:37,850 --> 01:51:40,820
我想你可能想去上學
I thought maybe you'd like to go back to school.

1368
01:51:45,890 --> 01:51:48,290
求你幫個忙，老板
I got a favor to ask you, boss.

1369
01:51:50,530 --> 01:51:52,260
沒問題
Sure.

1370
01:51:53,630 --> 01:51:55,620
什么事都行
Anything you want.

1371
01:51:57,330 --> 01:52:00,300
記得我爸是怎么幫埃克斯的么？
Remember what my daddy did for Axel?

1372
01:52:13,180 --> 01:52:15,650
想都不要想
Don't even think about that.

1373
01:52:19,520 --> 01:52:21,960
我不能象現在這樣，弗蘭基
I can't be like this, Frankie.

1374
01:52:25,200 --> 01:52:26,960
在我已經成就那么多以后
Not after what I done.

1375
01:52:27,130 --> 01:52:29,120
我見識了整個世界
I seen the world.

1376
01:52:32,200 --> 01:52:34,400
人們高呼我的名字
People chanted my name.

1377
01:52:35,410 --> 01:52:36,570
喔...
Well...

1378
01:52:38,510 --> 01:52:42,000
...不是我的本名 是你給我起的該死的名字
...not my name, some damn name you gave me.

1379
01:52:45,020 --> 01:52:47,480
可他們為我歡呼
But they were chanting for me.

1380
01:52:51,020 --> 01:52:53,390
我上過雜志
I was in magazines.

1381
01:52:57,160 --> 01:52:59,920
你以為我以前做過這樣的夢么？
You think I ever dreamed that'd happen?

1382
01:53:04,330 --> 01:53:08,000
我生出來的時候只有2磅1.5盎司
I was born at 2 pounds, 1 and a half ounces.

1383
01:53:11,440 --> 01:53:15,040
爸爸以前總說我是打拼 到這個世界上的...
Daddy used to tell me I fought to get into this world...

1384
01:53:18,380 --> 01:53:20,750
...我也會打出一片天地
...and I'd fight my way out.

1385
01:53:25,690 --> 01:53:28,620
那是我唯一想做的，弗蘭基
That's all I wanna do, Frankie.

1386
01:53:30,790 --> 01:53:33,260
我只是不想為那個和你打
I just don't wanna fight you to do it.

1387
01:53:36,200 --> 01:53:37,600
我得到了我要的
I got what I needed.

1388
01:53:41,570 --> 01:53:44,060
全部都得到了
I got it all.

1389
01:53:47,580 --> 01:53:50,640
別讓他們從我身邊一點點地拿走
Don't let them keep taking it away from me.

1390
01:53:55,720 --> 01:54:00,680
別讓我一直躺在這 直到聽不見人們的歡呼聲為止
Don't let me lie here till I can't hear those people chanting no more.

1391
01:54:05,660 --> 01:54:07,930
我不能
I can't.

1392
01:54:08,630 --> 01:54:10,730
求求你
Please.

1393
01:54:12,770 --> 01:54:15,260
拜托，不要求我
Please, don't ask me.

1394
01:54:17,370 --> 01:54:19,470
我在求呢
I'm asking.

1395
01:54:23,050 --> 01:54:24,950
我不能
I can't.

1396
01:55:08,830 --> 01:55:10,820
喂？
Hello?

1397
01:55:15,490 --> 01:55:17,930
午夜時分...
In the middle of the night...

1398
01:55:17,930 --> 01:55:21,430
...麥琪自己找到了辦法
...Maggie had found her own solution.

1399
01:55:21,490 --> 01:55:24,170
她咬舌了
She had bit her tongue.

1400
01:55:30,740 --> 01:55:34,110
停下來，停下來
Stop. Stop.

1401
01:55:37,040 --> 01:55:40,220
看著我，看著我
Look at me. Look at me.

1402
01:55:53,950 --> 01:55:58,150
差點失血過多而死 直到他們把她的傷口縫合
Nearly bled to death before they stitched her up.

1403
01:55:58,150 --> 01:56:02,830
在弗蘭基到來以前，她恢復了知覺 把縫上的傷口又撕開了
She came around and ripped them out before Frankie even got there.

1404
01:56:02,830 --> 01:56:05,180
他們又把傷口縫起來
They stitched her up again...

1405
01:56:05,180 --> 01:56:08,950
墊起了舌頭 以免她再咬舌自盡
...padded the tongue so she couldn't bite.

1406
01:56:26,730 --> 01:56:29,600
你不能那么做，你知道的
You can't do it, you know that.

1407
01:56:30,920 --> 01:56:33,410
我知道，神父
I do, Father.

1408
01:56:33,850 --> 01:56:35,990
可你不知道她有多遲鈍
But you don't know how thick she is...

1409
01:56:35,990 --> 01:56:38,970
訓練她有多難
...how hard it was to train her.

1410
01:56:38,970 --> 01:56:43,020
其他拳手你叫他們做什么 他們就做什么
Other fighters would do exactly what you'd say to them...

1411
01:56:43,020 --> 01:56:48,980
但她卻會問為什么這樣，為什么那樣 然后還是按自己的方式去做
...and she'd ask, why this and why that, and then do it her own way anyway.

1412
01:56:49,690 --> 01:56:51,920
她能去爭奪冠軍，我....
How she fought for the title, I...

1413
01:56:52,100 --> 01:56:53,620
不是靠任何....
It wasn't by anything...

1414
01:56:53,800 --> 01:56:56,820
不是靠聽我的話
Well, it wasn't by listening to me.

1415
01:57:05,880 --> 01:57:08,170
但是她現在想死
But now she wants to die...

1416
01:57:08,340 --> 01:57:10,570
而我只想把她留在我身邊
...and I just wanna keep her with me.

1417
01:57:14,920 --> 01:57:19,150
我向上帝起誓，神父
And I swear to God, Father, it's...

1418
01:57:19,620 --> 01:57:22,490
這樣做是犯罪
It's committing a sin by doing it.

1419
01:57:22,660 --> 01:57:26,060
讓她活下去，實際上是在殺死她
By keeping her alive, I'm killing her.

1420
01:57:26,500 --> 01:57:29,490
你明白我的意思么？ 我怎么才能克服呢？
Do you know what I mean? How do I get around that?

1421
01:57:30,830 --> 01:57:33,670
你不需要，你不要插手，弗蘭基
You don't. You step aside, Frankie.

1422
01:57:33,840 --> 01:57:35,770
把她交托給上帝
You leave her with God.

1423
01:57:36,440 --> 01:57:40,000
她沒有求上帝幫忙 她求我幫忙
She's not asking for God's help. She's asking for mine.

1424
01:57:40,180 --> 01:57:44,140
23年了，我基本上每天 都能在彌撒上見到你，弗蘭基
Frankie, I've seen you at Mass almost every day for 23 years.

1425
01:57:44,350 --> 01:57:46,340
只有那些為了某些事 而不能原諒自己的人
The only person comes to church that much...

1426
01:57:46,520 --> 01:57:48,180
才會這么頻繁地來教堂
...is the kind who can't forgive himself for something.

1427
01:57:48,350 --> 01:57:50,720
無論你身上背負著什么罪
Whatever sins you're carrying...

1428
01:57:51,220 --> 01:57:53,450
都無法和這個相提并論
...they're nothing compared to this.

1429
01:57:53,450 --> 01:57:58,220
忘記上帝，天堂和地獄吧
Forget about God or heaven and hell.

1430
01:57:58,390 --> 01:58:01,970
如果你那么做，你會迷失的
If you do this thing, you'll be lost.

1431
01:58:04,930 --> 01:58:07,200
深深地迷失
Somewhere so deep...

1432
01:58:09,010 --> 01:58:11,440
深到再也找不回自我了
...you'll never find yourself again.

1433
01:58:17,610 --> 01:58:20,050
我想我已經是了
I think I did it already.

1434
01:58:41,940 --> 01:58:45,270
我們一直給她鎮靜劑 好保證她不會再那么做
We're keeping her sedated so she won't try that again.

1435
01:59:50,470 --> 01:59:53,140
我今早去看了麥琪
I went to see Maggie this morning.

1436
01:59:54,880 --> 01:59:56,870
你一定是去了其他地方
You must have been somewhere else.

1437
01:59:58,050 --> 01:59:59,910
是啊
Yeah.

1438
02:00:03,750 --> 02:00:05,850
你在和一個我不認識的對手奮戰？
You got a fight I don't know about?

1439
02:00:11,260 --> 02:00:13,520
那不是你的錯
It wasn't your fault.

1440
02:00:13,960 --> 02:00:16,090
我當時那么說是錯誤的
I was wrong to say that.

1441
02:00:16,370 --> 02:00:18,300
你說得真對
You're damn right.

1442
02:00:19,700 --> 02:00:21,030
我給你找到一個拳手
I found you a fighter...

1443
02:00:21,200 --> 02:00:24,730
你讓她發揮出了最大的潛力
...and you made her the best fighter she could be.

1444
02:00:27,340 --> 02:00:28,780
我殺了她
I killed her.

1445
02:00:28,950 --> 02:00:30,810
別那么說
Don't say that.

1446
02:00:31,210 --> 02:00:33,740
麥琪走進那扇門的時候 除了膽量什么都沒有
Maggie walked through that door with nothing but guts.

1447
02:00:33,920 --> 02:00:37,110
根本沒有機會實現她的夢想
No chance in the world of being what she needed to be.

1448
02:00:37,290 --> 02:00:40,690
一年半以后，她在爭奪世界冠軍
A year and a half later, she's fighting for the championship of the world.

1449
02:00:40,860 --> 02:00:42,090
是你的功勞
You did that.

1450
02:00:44,330 --> 02:00:46,850
每天都有人死去的，弗蘭基
People die every day, Frankie.

1451
02:00:47,030 --> 02:00:48,900
拖地的時候，刷碗的時候
Mopping floors, washing dishes.

1452
02:00:49,230 --> 02:00:51,170
你知道他們最后一個念頭是什么嗎？
And you know what their last thought is?

1453
02:00:51,330 --> 02:00:53,800
“我從沒有過機會”
"I never got my shot."

1454
02:00:54,300 --> 02:00:56,600
因為有你，麥琪得到了屬于她的機會
Because of you, Maggie got her shot.

1455
02:00:57,840 --> 02:01:01,540
如果她今天就死去 你知道她最后一個念頭是什么嗎？
If she dies today, you know what her last thought will be?

1456
02:01:02,410 --> 02:01:04,780
“我覺得我干得不錯”
"I think I did all right."

1457
02:01:12,390 --> 02:01:14,950
我會覺得心安理得的
I know I could rest with that.

1458
02:01:17,630 --> 02:01:18,690
是啊
Yeah.

1459
02:01:19,260 --> 02:01:21,090
是啊
Yeah.

1460
02:01:32,140 --> 02:01:33,840
是啊
Yeah.

1461
02:02:12,120 --> 02:02:13,510
我去沖杯咖啡
I'm gonna get a cup of coffee.

1462
02:02:13,680 --> 02:02:15,170
好
Yeah.

1463
02:02:42,110 --> 02:02:43,740
好了
All right.

1464
02:02:47,920 --> 02:02:50,390
我會拔掉你的呼吸器...
I'm gonna disconnect your air machine...

1465
02:02:51,250 --> 02:02:53,520
...然后你就會睡著
...then you're gonna go to sleep.

1466
02:02:58,230 --> 02:03:00,960
然后我給你打一針，你就...
Then I'll give you a shot, and you'II...

1467
02:03:02,060 --> 02:03:03,660
...會一直睡下去
...stay asleep.

1468
02:03:09,010 --> 02:03:10,770
“莫 庫什勒”...
Mo cuishle...

1469
02:03:12,340 --> 02:03:15,900
...的意思是“我的摯愛，我的血肉”
...means "my darling, my blood."

1470
02:04:24,010 --> 02:04:26,810
他只給她打了一針
He gave her a single shot.

1471
02:04:27,180 --> 02:04:31,420
腎上腺素的劑量是需要量的好幾倍
It was enough adrenaline to do the job a few times over.

1472
02:04:31,750 --> 02:04:34,620
他不想讓她再受一次苦
He didn't want her going through this again.

1473
02:05:24,470 --> 02:05:26,170
然后他走出門去
Then he walked out.

1474
02:05:26,780 --> 02:05:30,080
我想他什么都沒有了
I don't think he had anything left.

1475
02:05:48,630 --> 02:05:50,860
我回到拳擊館
I went back to the gym.

1476
02:05:51,170 --> 02:05:54,830
等待著，認為他總有一天會回來
Waited, figuring he'd turn up sooner or later.

1477
02:06:14,460 --> 02:06:17,890
就在那時一個鬼魂走進門來
And that's when a ghost came through the door.

1478
02:06:20,430 --> 02:06:23,490
我想過你說的話了 斯科雷普先生
I got to thinking what you said, Mr.Scrap.

1479
02:06:24,570 --> 02:06:26,230
結果呢，丹吉爾？
What was that, Danger?

1480
02:06:27,840 --> 02:06:30,430
每個人都會失敗的
Anybody can lose one fight.

1481
02:06:31,670 --> 02:06:33,510
這是實話
That's the truth.

1482
02:06:34,340 --> 02:06:36,900
去吧，戴上手套 你已經很長時間沒訓練了
Go on, put your gloves on. You missed a lot of training.

1483
02:06:38,880 --> 02:06:41,350
好的，斯科雷普先生，沒問題
Will do, Mr.Scrap. Sure thing.

1484
02:07:00,170 --> 02:07:04,010
弗蘭基再也沒回來
Frankie never came back at all.

1485
02:07:05,910 --> 02:07:08,580
（兇狠是不夠的）

1486
02:07:18,090 --> 02:07:22,590
弗蘭基沒留下訊息 沒人知道他去了哪
Frankie didn't leave a note, and nobody knew where he went.

1487
02:07:22,590 --> 02:07:25,290
我希望他是去找你了
I'd hoped he'd gone to find you...

1488
02:07:25,290 --> 02:07:28,460
去再次請求你的原諒
...and ask you one more time to forgive him.

1489
02:07:28,460 --> 02:07:32,070
但也許他心中什么都沒有了
But maybe he didn't have anything left in his heart.

1490
02:07:32,070 --> 02:07:35,940
我只希望他能找到個地方 享受片刻的安寧
I just hope he found someplace where he could find a little peace.

1491
02:07:35,940 --> 02:07:39,380
一個雪松和橡樹環繞
A place set in the cedars and oak trees.

1492
02:07:39,380 --> 02:07:42,750
比偏僻更偏僻的地方
Somewhere between nowhere and goodbye.

1493
02:07:42,750 --> 02:07:46,820
但那可能只是一廂情愿
But that's probably wishful thinking.

1494
02:07:46,820 --> 02:07:49,350
無論他在哪兒
No matter where he is...

1495
02:07:49,350 --> 02:07:55,670
我想你該知道你父親 究竟是個什么樣的人
...I thought you should know what kind of man your father really was.

1496
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:00,200


1497
